Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:03:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}牛逼字幕,二雷制作{\r}\N(LEO修改版20131123)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.40,0:03:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}你为什么总是这样？{\r}\NWhy must you be this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.40,0:03:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k200}为什么我们总有分歧？ 这是个问题。{\r}\NWhy is there always a problem? It's a good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.40,0:03:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}你想回家吗？ 你想掉头回家吗？{\r}\NDo you want to go home? Do you want to turn around?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.50,0:03:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k210}- 是! - 那可是喜玛拉雅!{\r}\N- Yes! - It's the Himalayas!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.90,0:03:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}喜玛拉雅山，我和你谈论多久了？{\r}\NHow long have I been talking about the Himalayas?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.60,0:03:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k270}- 多久？ - 很久了。{\r}\N- How long? - Far too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.00,0:03:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}Horst,我们什么时候到, 你能快一点吗?{\r}\NHorst, when we get there, can you give me a hand, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}- 当然。 - Ingrid，安静一会！{\r}\N- Yes, of course. - Ingrid, stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.40,0:04:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我们一定要把这件事情做好。{\r}\NLet's try to make the best of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.40,0:04:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}那个想见我们的白痴在哪？{\r}\NWhere's thls idiot who's supposed to meet us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.60,0:04:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}劳驾!{\r}\NMove!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.80,0:04:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}Harrer 先生。{\r}\NMr. Harrer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.20,0:04:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k140}你的票在我这。{\r}\NI have your tickets.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.90,0:04:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k170}-我迟到了，带我去车厢吧。 - 哦，你误会了。{\r}\N- I'm late. Take me to my train. - No, you don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.90,0:04:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我是 Peter Aufschnaiter。 我是探险队的队长。{\r}\NI am Peter Aufschnaiter. I am leading the expedition.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.30,0:04:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}- 你好！ - 我们英雄在这里！{\r}\N- How do you do? - Here's our celebrity!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.50,0:04:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k220}Harrer 先生?{\r}\NMr. Harrer?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.50,0:04:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k200}Harrer 先生， 我以 Reichssportsfuhrer（德语：国家体委主任）的名义……{\r}\NMay I say, Mr. Harrer, on behalf of the Reichssportsfuhrer...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.50,0:04:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我们为探险队有这样的德国英雄而感到自豪！{\r}\Nwe are honored to have such a great German hero on the team.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.80,0:04:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}谢谢， 但是我是奥地利人。{\r}\NThank you, but I'm Austrian.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.30,0:04:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k250}我知道。 但是我确信—— 作为国家社会党的杰出代表{\r}\NYes. but I'm sure that . as a distinguished member...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.80,0:04:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k250}当你将国旗插上南迦帕尔巴特峰（Nanga Parbat）时，{\r}\Nof the National Soclalist Party, you would be proud to plant...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.90,0:05:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}你会感到自豪！{\r}\Nour country's flag on the summit of Nanga Parbat when you reach it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.00,0:05:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}Hans Lobenhoffer（人名）{\r}\NHans Lobenhoffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.00,0:05:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k200}Lutz Chicken（人名）{\r}\NLutz Chicken.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.50,0:05:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}和你漂亮的妻子合一张影。{\r}\NAnd a picture with your lovely wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.50,0:05:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}还有那位先生——嗯——{\r}\NAnd Mr.--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.00,0:05:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k150}Horst lmmendorf。好朋友。 没必要拍照了。{\r}\NHorst lmmendorf. Family frlend. No plcture necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.30,0:05:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}孩子什么时候出生？ Harrer夫人？{\r}\NWhen is the little one due. . Mrs. Harrer?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.30,0:05:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k200}大概是我丈夫到达营地的时候。{\r}\NAbout the time my husband reaches the base camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.50,0:05:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}谢谢。{\r}\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.90,0:05:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k240}你为什么不告诉那整个腐朽的国家我们的麻烦？{\r}\NWhy don't you tell the entire stinking country our troubles?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.30,0:05:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我要上车了。 你还有什么话想说？{\r}\NI'm getting on that train. Do you have anything you want to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.70,0:05:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}就这样吧。{\r}\NFine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.00,0:05:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k230}走吧！{\r}\NGo. Leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.80,0:05:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}四个月以后见。{\r}\NI'll see you in four months.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.20,0:05:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}-好好照顾她， Horst。 -没问题， Heinrich 。 。{\r}\N- Take good care of her, Horst. - I will. Heinrich . .
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.90,0:07:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我们行程5000英里，{\r}\NWe will travel 5,000 miles.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.60,0:07:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k270}到达印度， 然后动身去喜玛拉雅，{\r}\NWhen we reach lndia, we will head for the Hlmalayas...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.30,0:07:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k270}接着向世界第九高峰出发， 南迦帕尔巴特峰（Nanga Parbat）{\r}\Nand the ninth highest peak on Earth, Nanga Parbat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.30,0:07:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}德国称作“Unserberg-- 我们的山峰。”{\r}\NGermany calls it "Unserberg-- Our Mountain. "
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.10,0:07:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}在我们之前，四支德国探险队尝试过{\r}\NBefore us, four German expeditions attempted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.10,0:07:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}都失败了。{\r}\NAll failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.70,0:07:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k160}11名登山队员在风暴和雪崩中丧身。{\r}\NEleven climbers were killed in storms and avalanches.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.40,0:07:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}直到现在征服南迦帕尔巴特峰（Nanga Parbat） 还是这个国家的阴影--{\r}\NBy now, the conquest of Nanga Parbat is a national obsession--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.10,0:07:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}关系到德国的自尊{\r}\Na matter of German pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.90,0:07:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}1939年7月29日{\r}\NJuly 29, 1939.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.50,0:07:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k260}我们在海拔22000英尺的地方扎营。{\r}\NWe have already made Camp Four at 22.000 feet. .
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.40,0:08:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}头顶是 Reklak 冰河和难以攀登的冰崩（icefall）。{\r}\NOverhead is the Reklak Glacier and a difficult climb up the icefall.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.50,0:08:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}孩子已经一个月大了。{\r}\NThe baby must be at least one month old now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.70,0:08:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我感到困惑，心烦意乱。{\r}\NI have been so confused and dlstracted.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.10,0:08:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}不能象往常一样自信地攀登{\r}\NI can 't climb with my usual confldence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.50,0:08:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}你没事吧？{\r}\NAre you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:08:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}Shit!{\r}\NShit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.40,0:08:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}- 你没事吧？ - 要下来帮你吗？{\r}\N- Are you al I right? - Shall we come down?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.40,0:09:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}只是掉了个鞋钉。{\r}\NLost a crampon !
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.20,0:09:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k180}继续前进！{\r}\NGo ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.60,0:09:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}天气很糟， 大家应该用绳子绑在一起。{\r}\NThe weather's getting bad. We should rope up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.90,0:09:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}- 你受伤了吗？ - 只是擦伤， 我要走到前面去。{\r}\N- Did you hurt yourself back there? - Just a scratch. I'll lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.90,0:10:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}岩石！{\r}\NRocks!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.90,0:10:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k200}向下看！{\r}\NLook out below!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.40,0:10:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}抓住我！{\r}\NHold me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.50,0:10:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}你抓住我了吗?{\r}\NHave you got me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.40,0:10:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}抓住我！{\r}\NHold me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.20,0:11:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}你应该告诉我伤口的情况，{\r}\NYou should have told me how bad that wound was.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.30,0:11:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我就可以查看一下， 然后帮你缝合伤口。{\r}\NI should take a look at lt. I could sew it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.30,0:12:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}这不关你的事！{\r}\NIt's not your problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.00,0:12:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}事实上， 这就是我的事。{\r}\NActually, it is my problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.00,0:12:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k200}- 他关系到我的生命。 -什么？{\r}\N- It's my life. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.30,0:12:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}当你隐瞒你受重伤的事实时， 我的生命就置于危险之中{\r}\NWhen you conceal a serious injury and put my life at risk...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}所以那是我的事情。{\r}\NI consider th at my problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.00,0:12:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k200}不， 是你把自己的生命置于危险之中， 而我救了你！ 所以你给我闭嘴！{\r}\NNo, you put your life at rlsk. I saved it, so shut up !
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.20,0:12:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}Please, it is not your place--{\r}\NPlease, it is not your place--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.40,0:12:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k220}闭嘴！{\r}\NShut up !
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.80,0:12:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}如果下一次你还隐瞒伤情 那么 Heinrich。。。{\r}\NThe next time you lle about an lnjury, Heinrich...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.50,0:12:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}你将被开除。{\r}\Nyou're off the team.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.70,0:12:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}走着瞧。{\r}\NTry it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.10,0:13:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}8月4号， 五号营地。 强烈的风暴过去了{\r}\NAugust 4th, Camp Five. Some fierce storms have passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.90,0:14:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我的队友担心雪崩随时会发生{\r}\NMy teammates are nervous about the avalanches...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.90,0:14:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}于是我们不得不驻留几天。{\r}\Nso we 've been holed up for days.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.50,0:14:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k260}Aufschnalter 应该将营地扎在低谷，而不是在高处{\r}\NAufschnalter should take advantage of this lowland weather to make high camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.80,0:14:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}但是他不同意我的意见。 白痴！{\r}\NBut he disagrees with me. Fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.50,0:14:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}好像其他的队友都不介意在原地坐等{\r}\NIt seems the others don 't mind sitting here waiting...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.50,0:14:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}除了祈祷无事可做。{\r}\Nhoping, doing nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.40,0:14:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k290}太多的自问绝对不是一件好事{\r}\NSo much time to question one 's self is not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.70,0:14:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我开始认为这次探险是一个错误{\r}\NI am beginnlng to think this whole expedition was a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.30,0:14:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}快跑！ 雪崩！出来！{\r}\NRun ! Avalanche! Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.30,0:14:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}什么都不要带！{\r}\NLeave everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.30,0:15:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}把它放下！{\r}\NPut that down !
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.50,0:15:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我们现在要下山！{\r}\NWe are going down now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.30,0:15:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k180}如果他们害怕风暴，那就送他们去2号营地{\r}\NIf they're frightened of a storm, send them down to Camp Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.20,0:15:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k290}我可以一个人登顶！ Always give the best man his shot!{\r}\NI could summit on my own ! Always give the best man his shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.60,0:15:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}他想告诉我们他是最强的{\r}\NHe's trying to tell us he's the best man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.20,0:15:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k260}给我两个夏尔巴人（Sherpa登山能力超强的一个西藏种族） 今晚我就可以建立6号营地{\r}\NGive me two Sherpas. I can make Camp Six by tonight...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.50,0:15:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k230}明天我就登顶！{\r}\Nand my final attack tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.50,0:15:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k200}-我们必须整队下山！ - 那个顶峰是我的！{\r}\N- We are going down now as a team! - I've earned that peak!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.50,0:15:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}- 我渴望顶峰！ - 全队！ 这是命令！{\r}\N- I want th at peak! - As a team! That's an order!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.50,0:15:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k200}这是命令！ 命令！{\r}\NThat is an order! An order!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.30,0:15:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}跟着我！{\r}\NFollow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.10,0:16:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}达赖喇嘛的神像。会保护我们{\r}\NDalai Lama photo. Good protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.30,0:16:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}带着它， Si Hib， 它会保护你{\r}\NTake it. Si Hib. . It will protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.30,0:16:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}不，对我来说这毫无意义{\r}\NNo, that means nothing to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.70,0:16:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}达赖喇嘛。达赖喇嘛的神像{\r}\NDalai Lama. Dalai Lama photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.40,0:16:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k270}Si Hib，带着它{\r}\NSi Hib, take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.20,0:17:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k180}它会保护你{\r}\NGood protection for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.90,0:17:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}下午好， Herr Harrer{\r}\NGood afternoon, Herr Harrer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.60,0:17:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k270}嘿， 希望德国人从波兰撤退{\r}\NWell, let's hope that Germany retreats from Poland...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.80,0:17:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k220}象你们下山一样快{\r}\Nas quickly as you did from your mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.10,0:17:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k230}你现在应该进监狱呆会了{\r}\NIt might save you some prison time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.30,0:17:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}什么？你是谁？{\r}\NWhat is this? Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.30,0:17:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k200}- 我很抱歉，但是你被逮捕了 - 什么罪名？登顶失败？{\r}\N- I'm sorry, but you're under arrest. - What charge? Failure to summit?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.40,0:17:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}恐怕不是{\r}\NI'm afraid not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.00,0:17:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k260}你知道……不列颠王国已经向德国宣战{\r}\NYou see, war has been declared between Hls Majesty's Government and Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.30,0:17:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}所有大英帝国领土上的敌人 现在都是战俘了{\r}\NSo all enemy aliens on British Empire soil are now prisoners of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.10,0:18:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}-站住，否则开枪了！ - 举起手来！{\r}\N- Stop, or I'll shoot! - Hands up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.10,0:18:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}不，你们什么都不知道！ 我是奥地利人！ 我是登山队员！{\r}\NNo, you don't understand! I'm Austrian ! I'm a cllmber!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.90,0:18:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k280}我和你们的狗屁战争毫无关系{\r}\NI have nothing to do with your silly war!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.60,0:18:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}让我自己走！ 这是对我的侮辱！{\r}\NI can walk myself. This is an insult!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.00,0:18:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}你们以为可以逮捕我， 但是你们没有权利这样做！{\r}\NYou think you have the last word, but you don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.20,0:18:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}猪！ 都是猪！{\r}\NPigs! All of you, pigs!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.40,0:19:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}1939年10月15日{\r}\NOctober 15, 1939.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.10,0:19:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}抵达战俘营。我对自己说{\r}\NReaching prison camp, I make a promise to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.90,0:19:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}明年夏至之前我会回到 lngrid 身边{\r}\NI will be lying beside lngrid before the summer solstice of the new year.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.00,0:19:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}喜马拉雅山脉就在我们前方{\r}\NThe Hlmalayas are right in front of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.60,0:19:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k260}逃跑并不困难，并且可以隐没在群山之中{\r}\NIt will be easy to escape and get lost in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.50,0:19:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}第四次逃跑的尝试，并没有使我离成功跟近{\r}\NMy fourth escape attempt brings me no closer to my goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.10,0:19:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}这次你跑了多远？{\r}\NHow far did you get this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.50,0:19:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k240}唯一的成果是——在战俘营中我似乎成了一个名人{\r}\NAll I have achieved is a certaln dubious celebrity among the prisoners.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.40,0:20:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}要是手中的笔能够写出心里所想的该多好{\r}\NIf only my hand could express what is ln my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.70,0:20:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我听说卫兵会帮你寄信{\r}\NI hear the guards are mailing letters for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.10,0:20:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}是的{\r}\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.40,0:20:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k130}可以帮我寄这个吗？{\r}\NWould you mail these?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.40,0:20:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}谢谢{\r}\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.90,0:20:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k250}Hey, Heinrich, 你看过这本书吗？{\r}\NHey, Heinrich, have you read this book?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.30,0:20:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k240}是关于你的{\r}\NIt was checked out to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.90,0:21:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}- 我们得和你谈谈 - 关于什么？{\r}\N- We need to talk to you. - What about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.00,0:21:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}关于这些。{\r}\NAbout this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.00,0:21:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}难以置信。 你们打算什么时候行动？{\r}\NImpressive. When do you plan to leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.90,0:21:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k290}雨季结束后。 你呢？{\r}\NAfter monsoon season. And you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.80,0:21:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我想你们选择了我穿越西藏的路线{\r}\NI see you've chosen my route through Tibet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.90,0:21:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}几乎没有外国人在那条路上生还。 祝你们好运。{\r}\NThe few foreigners who have tried never came back. So, good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.90,0:21:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}-你愿意和我们一起行动吗？ - 为什么？{\r}\N- Would you like to come with us? - Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.30,0:21:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}毕竟，你是这里的越狱专家{\r}\NAfter all, you are the authority on jailbreak around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.50,0:21:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}- 你的经验将使我们受益{\r}\N- We could benefit from your experience. - Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.70,0:21:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}停止这个尴尬的游戏吧{\r}\NStop this embarrassing charade.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.50,0:21:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}每次你逃跑之后， 巡逻的卫兵都会是原来的两三倍{\r}\NEvery time you escape, the patrols are doubled and tripled.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.40,0:21:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}对于我们中的其他人而言，这使生活变得非常困难{\r}\NIt is making life very difficult for the rest of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.70,0:21:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我更喜欢一个人旅行， 不过还是谢谢你的忠告。{\r}\NI prefer to travel on my own, but thanks for thinking of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.40,0:22:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}邮递员来过了。{\r}\NThe mailman has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.20,0:22:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}亲爱的Heinrlch:{\r}\NDear Heinrlch:
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.90,0:22:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k170}请在随信附上的离婚协议上签字，并寄给我的律师{\r}\NPlease sign the enclosed dlvorce papers and send them to my lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.60,0:22:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}Horst和我打算在我们的离婚手续办妥之后立刻结婚{\r}\NHorst and I intend to be married as soon as the divorce is flnalized.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.80,0:22:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}至于你的来信我收到了{\r}\NAs for your letter, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.80,0:22:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k200}你的儿子 Rolf Harrer 在你登山的时候出生的{\r}\NYour son, Rolf Harrer, was born while you were climbing the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.80,0:23:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}现在两岁了，喊 Horst 爸爸{\r}\NHe is now two years old and calls Horst "papa. "
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.80,0:23:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}当他足够大的时候 我会告诉他{\r}\NWhen he is old enough, I will tell him...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.10,0:23:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k230}他的生父在喜马拉雅山失踪了。{\r}\Nhis real father was lost in the Himalayas.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.80,0:23:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k270}由于你从来都没想过要这个孩子{\r}\NIt seems the kindest thing to say consldering...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.90,0:23:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k210}我想这是最好的方式告诉孩子关于他父亲的故事{\r}\Nyou never wanted the child anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.40,0:23:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k250}不必说了，我不打算{\r}\NNeedless to say, I have no intention...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.10,0:23:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k270}象你说的那样去解决我们自己的分歧了{\r}\Nof "resolving our differences " as you suggested.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.90,0:23:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}他们在你离开奥地利的时候都已经解决了{\r}\NThey were resolved the moment you left Austria.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.40,0:23:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我很难过你在印度被监禁{\r}\NI'm sorry you have been imprisoned ln lndia...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.70,0:23:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}并且希望这场可恶的战争 象所有人希望的那样早日结束{\r}\Nand hope this dreadful war will soon be over for everyone's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.90,0:23:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}Ingrid。{\r}\NIngrid.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.70,0:24:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我和你们一起走{\r}\NI'm coming with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.80,0:25:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}这是你们的计划？{\r}\NThis is your plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.30,0:25:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}以我的拙见，这很荒谬{\r}\NIn my humble opinion, this is ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.50,0:25:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}既然这样， 我们不会征求你的意见{\r}\NThen since you are so humble, we won't ask your opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.00,0:26:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}打开地图，转过身去{\r}\NOpen the charts. Turn around.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.30,0:26:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k230}背对大门 打开地图！{\r}\NKeep your back to the gate. Open the charts!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.50,0:26:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}一直说话， 按我的信号行动{\r}\NKeep talking. Wait for my signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.80,0:26:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}警报解除。 Okay。{\r}\NWe are clear. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.30,0:26:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}开门!{\r}\NOpen the gates!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.50,0:26:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}看这个。 开门!{\r}\NSee to this. Open the gates!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.30,0:27:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我一个人逃。{\r}\NI'm going off on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.30,0:27:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k200}祝你们好运{\r}\NSo, good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.00,0:28:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}第一次越狱 1939年11月18日{\r}\NFirst escape from prlson camp, November 18, 1939.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.90,0:28:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}Rolf Harrer--三个半月大{\r}\NRolf Harrer-- three and a half months old.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.40,0:28:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}1941年7月6日30岁生日{\r}\NMy 30th birthday, July 6, 1941.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.50,0:28:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}Rolf Harrer-- 正好一岁, 11个月零26天{\r}\NRolf Harrer-- exactly one year, 11 months and 26 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.80,0:28:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}最后一次从Dehra Dun越狱 Rolf Harrer--{\r}\NLast escape from Dehra Dun. Rolf Harrer--
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.40,0:31:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}吃两片药睡一觉就好了 天亮的时候我会给你送钱来的。{\r}\NTake two and sleep it off. I'll send you a bill in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.70,0:31:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}你在这里干什么？{\r}\NWhat are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.70,0:31:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k200}我很想念你 所以我就来拜访你{\r}\NI missed you so much. I thought I'd pay you a visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.90,0:31:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}其他的人呢？{\r}\NWhat about the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.40,0:31:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k250}出了 Nelang 意大利人就被抓住了。{\r}\NThe ltalians were caught outside Nelang.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.10,0:31:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k270}Lutz 和 Hans 病了 不得不回去。{\r}\NLutz and Hans got sick and had to turn back.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.20,0:31:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}- 我很难过听到这些。 - 我相信你说的是真的。{\r}\N- Sorry to hear that. - I'm sure you're heartbroken.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.80,0:31:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我可以在这里扎营过夜吗？{\r}\NMay I impose upon your generous nature and camp here tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.90,0:31:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}荣幸之至{\r}\NBe my guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.90,0:31:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k200}谢谢{\r}\NThank you. It is very gracious of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.50,0:32:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}你在这里还干些什么？{\r}\N- Good. - What else do you have in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.50,0:32:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k200}组织一个管弦乐团？{\r}\NA ten-piece orchestra?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.80,0:32:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k230}我听说日本人撤退了{\r}\NBy the way, I heard the Japanese have retreated...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.30,0:32:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}已经在退往上海的路上了{\r}\Nall the way back to Shanghai so even if you make it to the Chinese border...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.40,0:32:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}所以即使现在你在中国的边境上， 你也很难追上他们了{\r}\Nyou may have dlfficulty catchlng up with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.50,0:32:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k210}我不关心这些，哪怕他们向东京撤退{\r}\NI don 't care if they're repelled all the way back to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.20,0:32:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k270}如果想回奥地利，你就该关心{\r}\NYou should if you want to get back to Austria.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.10,0:32:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k290}- 但是我不想。 - 什么？{\r}\N- But I don't. - Don't what?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.60,0:32:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}- 回家。 - 为什么不？{\r}\N- Plan to go back. - Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.60,0:32:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}没有理由。{\r}\NNo particular reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.60,0:32:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}你回去的时候， 告诉我妻子{\r}\NWhen you get there, tell my wife...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.40,0:32:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k180}四年的婚姻和两年的监狱生活没什么区别{\r}\Nthat two years in prison camp is roughly equivalent to four years of marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.50,0:32:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我很高兴能同时逃出两座围城{\r}\NAnd I'm glad to be free of them both.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.10,0:33:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我也不会回去，即使该死的战争结束了{\r}\NI'm not golng back either, not until this shameful war is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.40,0:33:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}- 那你准备去哪？ - 西藏{\r}\N- And where are you headed? - Tibet.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.20,0:33:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k280}然后去中国， 看能不能在那里找到工作{\r}\NThen on to China. . see if I can find some work there.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.00,0:33:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}你呢？{\r}\NAnd you ?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.40,0:33:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k140}按照我的计算，这里离中国的边境有2058公里{\r}\NBy my calculations, the Chinese border is 2,058 kilometers away.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.00,0:33:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}离西藏68公里{\r}\NTibet is 68.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.60,0:33:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k260}你不可能带那么多东西走那么远{\r}\NIt's a long way to travel with such a heavy load.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.90,0:33:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}不多，全是食品{\r}\NNo, just full of food.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.30,0:33:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k240}- 听起来不错 - 嗯{\r}\N- Precisely. - Mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.90,0:33:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}这太糟了。{\r}\NThat's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.50,0:33:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k160}那些山脉反复无常（经常有雪崩）。 还有冰河要穿越{\r}\NThose mountains are treacherous. There are glaciers to be crossed.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.40,0:33:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}如果你和我绑在一起 我能保证你活着{\r}\NIf you had roped up to me, I could have kept you alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.70,0:33:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k230}考虑到最后一次绑在一起登山时你的表现{\r}\NConsidering your performance the last time we roped up...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.10,0:33:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k240}没有你我更安全{\r}\NI think I'm safer without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.60,0:33:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}那好！{\r}\NOf course.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.30,0:33:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我想你算错了， 关于这里离西藏边界有多远{\r}\NBut I think you are wrong about that Tibetan border calculatlon.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.60,0:34:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}按照我的计算是65公里{\r}\NBy my measurements, it is 65 kilometers.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.10,0:34:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}赌一公斤食品？{\r}\NCare to wager a kilo of food on that?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.90,0:34:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}可你只有一些烂饼干{\r}\NAll you've got is some stale crackers.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.30,0:34:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}但是我是对的。 我会赢。{\r}\NBut I'm right. I'll win.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.60,0:35:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}西藏，世界屋脊{\r}\NTibet, the roof of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.50,0:35:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k290}感觉就像登上了一座中世纪的城堡{\r}\NIt feels as though we have ascended a medieval stone fortress...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.70,0:35:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}高耸在亚洲中心{\r}\Ntowering above the center of Asla.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.60,0:35:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k290}这是地球上最高的地区{\r}\NThis ls the highest country on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.20,0:35:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k260}也是最孤独的{\r}\NAnd the most isolated.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.10,0:35:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}到了。{\r}\NThere it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.70,0:35:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k260}西藏{\r}\NTibet.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.70,0:35:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}- 正好68公里 - 恭喜{\r}\N- Exactly 68 kilometers. - Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.80,0:35:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}不幸的是你已经把你赢的都吃光了{\r}\NUnfortunately, you've eaten all your winnings.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.20,0:35:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}yes{\r}\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.50,0:35:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k130}只管笑，然后说yes 这样最好{\r}\NJust smile and say yes. It's better that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.10,0:36:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}这是你在监狱里学到的？令人吃惊{\r}\NIt's amazing what you learn in prison, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.20,0:36:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}西藏。{\r}\NTibet.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.40,0:36:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}- 外国人不能入藏 - oh，please!{\r}\N- No foreigners allowed in Tlbet. - Oh, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.10,0:36:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k270}外国人不能入藏!{\r}\NNo foreigner!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.70,0:36:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k160}Oh, please!{\r}\NOh, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.80,0:36:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}Yes。 Thank you。 Of course。{\r}\NYes. Thank you. Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.60,0:37:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我们不需要翻译{\r}\NNo translation needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.10,0:37:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}有些人看见我们很高兴{\r}\NSome people are glad to see us.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.50,0:37:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k240}别被它迷惑了。。。{\r}\NDon't let it get to your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.80,0:37:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k230}。。。藏族人拍手代表驱赶邪恶的力量{\r}\NWhen the Tibetans clap hands, it means they are driving out evil forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.10,0:37:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}给我们一些吃的{\r}\NWe need to find food.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.50,0:38:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}这是个预言。。。{\r}\NIt is the prophecy. It says here...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.20,0:38:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}十三世达赖喇嘛在他的遗嘱中说。。。{\r}\Nin the final testament of great thirteenth Dalai Lama.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.40,0:38:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}西藏的宗教和政府。。。{\r}\N"It may happen that, in Tibet, religions and government...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.30,0:38:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}将来会受到异族的威胁。{\r}\Nwill be attacked by outside forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.10,0:38:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k280}如果我们不能保护西藏。。。{\r}\NUnless we can guard our own country...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.50,0:38:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}。。。喇嘛和寺庙将有灭顶之灾;{\r}\Nmonks and their monasteries will be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.80,0:38:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我们的土地和财产将被剥夺;{\r}\NThe lands and property of government officials will be seized.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.60,0:38:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}达赖喇嘛和他所有的信徒。。。{\r}\NThe Dalai Lama an d all the revered holders of the faith...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.50,0:38:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}。。。都将消失,隐匿。{\r}\Nwill disappear and become nameless."
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.10,0:38:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k260}现在你知道我们为什么不欢迎外国人了?{\r}\NNow you understand why we are not welcome to forelgners here?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.90,0:38:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}是的，但是你们应该知道 我们并不是来威胁、伤害你们的{\r}\NYes, but you must understand we're not here to threaten or harm.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.10,0:38:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我们只想要点食物，然后上路……{\r}\NWe just need food, and then we'll be on our--
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.40,0:38:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k230}Garpon（探子）来了{\r}\NHis Excellency, the Garpon.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.80,0:39:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}尊敬的阁下, 很高兴见到你们{\r}\NYour Eminence, we're happy to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.50,0:39:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我们想道歉{\r}\NWe wanted to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.50,0:39:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}道歉。{\r}\NApologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.10,0:39:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}还想给你们这个特殊的礼物{\r}\NAnd give you this really special gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.80,0:39:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我们的心意{\r}\NPlease, from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.90,0:39:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k210}达赖喇嘛万岁{\r}\NLong live the Dalai Lama, Hi s Holiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.10,0:39:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}谢谢你们的圣像， 回印度去吧{\r}\NThank you for the picture. Go back to lndla!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.60,0:39:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}进入西藏西部边境两天之后 我们被体面地赶了出来{\r}\NTwo days into Tibet 's western frontier and we are graciously klcked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.10,0:39:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}向导押送我们。。。{\r}\NOur guides have strict orders to escort us...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.40,0:39:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k230}直到我们进入印度边境40公里{\r}\Nto the lndian border some 40 kllometers away...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.60,0:39:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}如果我们企图逃跑他们就会开枪{\r}\Nand to shoot us if we attempt escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.20,0:40:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我想这表示打招呼{\r}\NMust mean hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.40,0:40:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k220}只要他们不来亲我。{\r}\NAs long as they don't try to kiss me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.90,0:40:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}－我们必须补充给养。 －我破产了。{\r}\NWe have to stock up. I'm broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.90,0:40:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}别看我。{\r}\NDon't look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.90,0:40:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k200}我们必须吃点东西了,Peter。 知道现在几点了吗?{\r}\NWe have to eat. Peter. . Know what time it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.60,0:40:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}没得商量。{\r}\NIt is not negotiable.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.10,0:40:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k250}那是我登上Blanc山时我爸爸给我的礼物{\r}\NMy father gave it to me when I climbed Mount BI anc.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.60,0:40:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k250}每个人都登过Blanc山。{\r}\NEveryone's climbed Mount Blanc.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.80,0:40:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k220}如果我有一块这样的手表, 现在我会把它卖了的。{\r}\NIf I had a watch like this, I would trade it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.80,0:41:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}-这件甲克从哪来的? - 西藏北边。{\r}\N- Where did you get this jacket? - North Tibet.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.30,0:41:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k250}从中国来的共产主义战士非常好。{\r}\NCommunlsm soldier come from Chin a. Very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.90,0:41:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k260}他们分食物、发钱。 共产主战士。{\r}\NThey give food, money. Very nice. Communism soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.50,0:41:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}你喜欢军装，是吗？{\r}\NYou like military uniforms, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.00,0:41:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我送你一双德国军用鞋子好吗？{\r}\NI have German army boots. For you. Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.90,0:41:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}等一会。{\r}\NWait.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.90,0:42:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}给我这个, 防滑用的{\r}\NGive me these, for the guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.60,0:42:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k270}Look!{\r}\NLook!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.20,0:42:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}就是这样。 你喜欢吗?{\r}\NLike this. You like?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.50,0:42:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}非常好。 很实用的{\r}\NVery good. They're tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.50,0:42:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k200}哥们, 你想知道德国士兵怎么走路吗？{\r}\NMy friend, shall I show you how German soldiers march?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.50,0:42:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}你脸上必须是这种表情。{\r}\NYou must make this face.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.90,0:42:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}走! 对了。{\r}\NCome! Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.40,0:42:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k250}停!{\r}\NStop!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.90,0:42:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}非常好。你还需要练习{\r}\NExcellent. Yes. You, with practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.90,0:42:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}现在, 我向你演示德国士兵怎是么跑的。{\r}\NNow, I will show you how German soldiers run.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.10,0:43:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}先这样站好。{\r}\NStand like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.30,0:43:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}看什么呢?{\r}\NGuess what?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.90,0:43:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}没人了。{\r}\NAll clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.60,0:44:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}知道现在几点了?{\r}\NKnow what time it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.80,0:44:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}你以为和你一起走我很快乐。。。{\r}\NYou think I'm so happy to be traveling with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.20,0:44:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}而且我要为此买单?{\r}\NI should foot the bill?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.90,0:44:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k270}你好强呀，你就什么也不用贡献？{\r}\NYou are such a blg man you don't need to contribute?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.40,0:44:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}怎么了?{\r}\NYou have a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.10,0:44:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k170}告诉我。。。{\r}\NRemind me...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.70,0:44:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k260}在刚才那个集市你怎么说的。{\r}\Nwhat you said at the bazaar back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.80,0:44:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}"如果我有一块这样的手表，现在我会把它卖了。"{\r}\N"If I had a watch like that, I would trade it."
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.50,0:44:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}你确实没有一块。{\r}\NYou do not have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.40,0:44:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k290}骗子! 你有三块!{\r}\NYou cheap, lying bastard! You have three!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.80,0:45:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}这是从意大利战俘拿来的垃圾。{\r}\NThis is junk from some ltalian prisoners.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.30,0:45:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k250}不要和我解释!{\r}\NI don't give a shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.80,0:45:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k250}你听说过原则吗?{\r}\NHaven't you ever heard of a principle?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.00,0:45:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k220}什么原则?{\r}\NWhat principle?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.60,0:45:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k260}你想要一块手表? 捡一块走。。。。{\r}\NYou want a watch? Go ahead. Pick one.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.60,0:45:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}- 。。。遵守你原则去吧。 - 看看你自己 !{\r}\N- And keep your principles. - Look at you !
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.60,0:45:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}自私、乳臭未干、自以为是{\r}\NCaught being a selfish brat and you're gloating !
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.80,0:45:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}你像个女人。 你想要什么?{\r}\NYou're acting like an old woman. What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.80,0:45:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}试着道歉。{\r}\NTry apologizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.20,0:45:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}试着去反省{\r}\NTry feeling a little remorse.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.40,0:45:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k220}如果这些你都做不到, 那就试着去把你脸上的傻笑擦掉！{\r}\NAnd if all else fail s, try wiping that smirk off your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.90,0:45:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}拿着你的手表，然后给我闭嘴。{\r}\NTake your stinking watch and shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.70,0:45:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我不再想听到烦人的说教{\r}\NI don't need another boring sermon from some frustrated glorified tour guide.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.60,0:46:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}毫无疑问你永远是孤独的。{\r}\NNo wonder you are always alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.00,0:46:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k240}没有人可以忍受可怜的你{\r}\NNo one can stand your miserable company.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.20,0:46:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}拿着吧。{\r}\NPlease, take them.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.70,0:46:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}是我错了把它们藏起来。{\r}\NIt was wrong of me to hide them.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.30,0:47:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}- 拿着。 - 不。{\r}\N- Keep this. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.20,0:47:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我也不该得到它。 走吧。{\r}\NI didn't deserve It either. Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.60,0:47:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}他现在应该三岁半了。{\r}\NHe'll be three and a half years old now.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.90,0:47:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}不久她就会告诉他， 我在喜马拉雅山失踪了{\r}\NPretty soon, she'll tell him I was lost in the Himalayas.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.70,0:47:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}这真不错。{\r}\NWhich is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.10,0:47:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}为什么?{\r}\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.80,0:47:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}一个死去的爸爸总比不负责的爸爸好{\r}\NBetter a dead father than a lousy father.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.70,0:47:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}给他写封信。{\r}\NWrite him a letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.10,0:48:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}让他知道你还活着。{\r}\NLet him know you're still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.10,0:48:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}纽约。{\r}\NNew York.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.00,0:48:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}威尼斯。{\r}\NVenice.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.30,0:48:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}- 巴黎。 - Your Holiness, 你在哪里?{\r}\N- Paris. - Your Holiness, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.50,0:48:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}你该上课了。{\r}\NIt ls time for your lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.00,0:48:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}Your Holiness,你在哪里? 你该上课了。{\r}\NYour Holiness, where are you? It is time for your lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.10,0:48:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}亲爱的 Rolf Harrer:{\r}\NDear Rolf Harrer:
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.70,0:48:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k260}我是一个你不认识的人。。。{\r}\NI'm a person you don 't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.00,0:48:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k230}一个你从未遇见过的人。{\r}\Na man you 've never met.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.90,0:48:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k290}但你却萦绕我的脑海。。。{\r}\NBut you are someone who occupies my mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.70,0:48:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k280}。。。占据我的心灵。。。{\r}\Nand my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.70,0:48:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k200}尽管我们相隔万里。{\r}\Nin this dlstant land where I have gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.90,0:49:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}如果你可以想象地球上一个被悄悄隐藏在。。。{\r}\NIf you can imagine a hidden place tucked safely away from the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.90,0:49:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}。。。高耸的城墙和雪山之下;{\r}\Nconcealed by walls of high, snowcapped mountains--
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.40,0:49:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}充满着梦幻般美景的地方。{\r}\Na place rich with all the strange beauty of your nighttime dreams--
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.70,0:49:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}那就是现在我脚下的这片土地。{\r}\Nthen you know where I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.60,0:49:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}－西藏。。。{\r}\NIn the country where I am traveling, Tibet...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.40,0:49:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k280}那里的人们相信, 如果不远万里前去朝圣。。。{\r}\Npeople believe if they walk long distances to holy places...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.90,0:49:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}。。。所犯的罪孽将得到宽恕。{\r}\NIt purifles the bad deeds they've committed.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.80,0:49:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k290}而且他们相信朝圣的路途越艰险。。。{\r}\NThey believe the more difficult the journey...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.40,0:49:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k260}心灵的净化就越彻底。{\r}\Nthe greater the depth of purification.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.40,0:49:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我从一个遥远的地方前往另一个遥远的圣地。。。{\r}\NI've been walking from one faraway place to the next for many years--
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.40,0:49:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}。。。路途象生命一样漫长。{\r}\Nas long as you have lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.70,0:49:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我看见高原上四季变迁,{\r}\NI have seen seasons change across the high plateaus.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.30,0:49:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}看见冬天藏野驴向南迁徙。。。{\r}\NI have seen wild kiangs migrate south in winter...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.60,0:49:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}。。。当春天的来临时候他们悄悄又回来。{\r}\Nand sweep back across the fields when spring appears.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.50,0:49:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}在这里只要时间存在。。。{\r}\NIn this place, where time stands still...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.10,0:50:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k260}。。。一切似乎都在变化,{\r}\Nit seems that everything is moving...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.00,0:50:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k290}包括我自己。{\r}\Nincluding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.30,0:50:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我不知道自己要去哪里。。。{\r}\NI can 't say I know where I'm going...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.30,0:50:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k200}也不知道罪孽是否会被宽恕。{\r}\Nnor whether my bad deeds can be purified.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.80,0:50:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我后悔很多过去的事情,{\r}\NThere are so many things I have done which I regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.00,0:50:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}但是当我达到那个遥远的终点时, 我希望你能明白。。。{\r}\NBut when I come to a full stop, I hope you will understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.90,0:50:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}。。。我们之间的距离并不象看起来那么遥远。{\r}\Nthat the distance between us is not as great as it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.20,0:50:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}深爱你的爸爸{\r}\NWlth deep affection...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.10,0:50:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k190}Heinrlch Harrer。{\r}\Nyour father, Heinrlch Harrer.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.60,0:50:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}起来。{\r}\NGet up.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.20,0:50:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}上帝!{\r}\NMy God!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.50,0:50:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我把这个给你。{\r}\NI'll give you these.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.80,0:51:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}黄头发!{\r}\NYellow head!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.20,0:51:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k240}- No! Wait! 我们一无所有! - 把钱交出来!{\r}\N- No! Wait! We have nothing! - Give me money!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.20,0:51:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我们没有钱!{\r}\NWe have no money!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.70,0:51:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k150}手表也行!{\r}\NGive me watch !
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.70,0:51:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k200}-把衣服给我! - 我们什么也没有 !{\r}\N- Give me clothes! - We have nothing for you !
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.70,0:52:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}等一会!{\r}\NWait!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.30,0:52:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}你们去哪里?{\r}\NWhere are you headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.80,0:52:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我有通行证。{\r}\NI have permit.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.00,0:53:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}拉萨。 我有通行证。{\r}\NLhasa. I have permit.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.40,0:53:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}对于西藏的精神领袖来说窥看他的人民是不体面的。{\r}\NIt is unseemly for the spiritual leader of Tibet to spy on people.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.50,0:54:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}就在一个月前, 我们几乎死在强盗手里。{\r}\NOnly a month ago, we were certain of death at the hands of bandits.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.60,0:54:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}而今天我们已经来到了禁城－拉萨的大门。{\r}\NAnd today, we have reached the gates of the forbidden city of Lhasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.40,0:54:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}它象麦加一样难以企及并且充满诱惑。。。{\r}\NIt is as difficult a goal as Mecca...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.30,0:54:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k290}因为它的大门从不向任何外国人开放。{\r}\Nand preclsely as attractive because it ls closed to all foreigners.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.40,0:54:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}即使在如此糟糕的情况之下。。。{\r}\NEven in our miserable condition...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.90,0:54:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k250}。。。我们依然能感到圣城拉萨的诱惑{\r}\Nwe feel the lure of Tlbet 's holiest city...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.00,0:54:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}那里是达赖喇嘛的家。{\r}\Nhome of the Dalai Lama.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.30,0:54:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}只有很少的外国人得以洞察她的神秘。{\r}\NOnly a few foreigners had penetrated its mysteries.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.30,0:55:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}哦, 上帝!{\r}\NOh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.20,0:55:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}-结束了? -没有。{\r}\N- Is It over? - No. it is not over. .
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.50,0:56:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}如果你们愿意的话可以留下来吃午饭。{\r}\NYou are invited to stay for lunch, if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.70,0:56:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我们非常愿意。{\r}\NWe'd like that very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.00,0:56:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我是 Tsarong。 欢迎来我家。{\r}\NI am Tsarong. Welcome to my home.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.80,0:56:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k280}我叫 Peter。{\r}\NI am Peter.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.70,0:56:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}Lord Chamberlain(官名,宫务大臣), 我可以见。。。{\r}\NLord Chamberlain, may I request...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.00,0:56:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k230}the Regent(摄政者) 和 the Minister of the cabinet(内阁大臣)吗?{\r}\Nan audlence with the regent and ministers of the cabinet?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.70,0:56:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}关于两个来到西藏的外国人。{\r}\NIt's about two foreigners who came to Lhasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.10,0:57:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}尊敬的 Rinpoche。。。{\r}\NWith respect, Rinpoche...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.00,0:57:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k290}如果你的意图是阻止中国人以联盟国的名义征兵。。。{\r}\NIf your intention is to stop the Chinese from recruiting political allies...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.20,0:57:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}。。。然后要求他们停止向僧侣行贿{\r}\Nthen demanding that they stop trying to bribe monks...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.70,0:57:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}这不是最有效的策略。{\r}\Nis not the most effective tactic.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.40,0:57:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我是在向大臣征求意见, 而不是一个小小的秘书。{\r}\NI asked the opinion of the ministers, not that of a mere secretary.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.00,0:57:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}当然。 原谅我的无礼。{\r}\NOf course. Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.60,0:57:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}你可以离开了。{\r}\NYou may leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.50,0:57:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k190}把信件翻译出来。{\r}\NStart translating the letter as written .
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.10,0:57:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}好的。{\r}\NOf course.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.90,0:58:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}你知道有几个人可以从这样残酷的经历中幸存?{\r}\NDo you realize how many men could survive such an ordeal?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.20,0:58:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我们应该尊重他们。{\r}\NWe should respect them.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.30,0:58:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k210}如果我们把他们送回印度, 他们肯定又会回到监狱。{\r}\NIf we return them to lndla, they'll surely go back to prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.40,0:58:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}但是他们在这里毫无目的, Kungo Tsaron, 也无处可住。{\r}\NBut they have no purpose here, Kungo Tsarong. No place to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.80,0:58:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我已经邀请他们在我家的客房住下了。。。{\r}\NI have invited them to stay at my guest quarters...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.70,0:58:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我想你也一定会允许他们留在拉萨的。{\r}\Nassuming you would grant them permission to remain in Lhasa, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.10,0:58:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}邀请他们在你家住?{\r}\NInvited them to stay at your place?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.60,0:58:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}为什么?{\r}\NBut why?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.10,0:58:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k150}帮助困境中的人需要理由吗?{\r}\NMust one have reason to help those in need?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.30,0:58:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}Beast。{\r}\NBeast.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.60,0:58:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}她说你很臭。{\r}\NI think she said you stink.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.70,0:59:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}你们用不着自我介绍,{\r}\NYou do not need to introduce yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.60,0:59:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k290}我知道你们是谁。{\r}\NI know who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.40,0:59:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k280}我叫 Pema Lhaki。{\r}\NI am Pema Lhaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.70,0:59:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k230}Ngawang 想给你们一个礼物, 所以请把衣服脱了。{\r}\NNgawang wishes to make a gift to you, so please take your clothes off.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.70,0:59:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}快一点, 我不会给你们一整天时间。{\r}\NLet's get started. I don't have all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.00,0:59:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k230}哦, Ngawang Jigme真是太客气了。{\r}\NWell, this is most kind of Ngawang Jigme.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.40,0:59:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}他想关心谁呢?{\r}\NWho is he to be so thoughtful?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.90,0:59:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k250}总理的秘书。。。{\r}\NSecretary to the ministers of the government.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.40,0:59:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k250}。。。想给你们一套新衣服作为礼物。{\r}\NHe wished to make you a gift of new clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.20,0:59:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k280}请选一下你们喜欢的式样。{\r}\NPlease select your preferred article of clothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.80,0:59:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}你是裁缝?{\r}\NYou're a seamstress?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.50,0:59:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k170}我是裁缝, 拉萨唯一的裁缝。。。{\r}\NI am a tailor, sir, the only tailor in Lhasa...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.70,1:00:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}。。。曾经去过加尔各答 能够缝制一些简单的衣服。{\r}\Nwho has been to Calcutta and can reproduce these silly costumes.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.20,1:00:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我挑了?{\r}\NSo, I pick?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.20,1:00:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}嗯,随便哪件都可以。{\r}\NYes, choose whichever you like.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.50,1:00:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}- 这些你都会做? - 是的。{\r}\N- And you can make any of these? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.60,1:00:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}- 太好了。 - 你自己做的?{\r}\N- Very good. - Did you make this?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.60,1:00:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}-是的。 - 很漂亮。{\r}\N- Yes. - Beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.90,1:00:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}- 谢谢。 - 你喜欢这个吗?{\r}\N- Th ank you. - Do you like this?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.70,1:00:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k180}只要你喜欢。{\r}\NWhichever you like.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.70,1:00:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我想要这件漂亮的斜纹呢夹克,{\r}\NI will have this handsome tweed jacket.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.50,1:00:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k280}和这条软呢运动裤子。{\r}\NAnd this pair of sporting woolen trousers, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.20,1:00:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}- 非常好的选择。 - 谢谢。{\r}\N- Good choice. - Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.60,1:00:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k240}你呢, 先生?{\r}\NAnd you, sir?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.20,1:00:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}- 或许你可以为我挑选。 - 谢谢。{\r}\N- Perhaps you could choose for me. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.00,1:00:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}请脱掉藏袍。 我要量一下。{\r}\NPlease, sir, take off your chu-pa. I would like to measure.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.40,1:01:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}请站直。{\r}\NStand still, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.30,1:01:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}这边。{\r}\NThls way, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.80,1:01:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}- 请站直。 -对不起。{\r}\N- Stand still. - Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.70,1:01:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}-不要动。 -对不起。{\r}\N- No moving, please. - I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.00,1:01:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}这样你就不会掉下来。 完美。{\r}\NThat way, you will never fall. It's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.40,1:01:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k240}为了爬山而爬山不是有点傻吗? Heinrich。{\r}\NStill, walking up mountain s is a fool's pleasure, Heinrich.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.10,1:01:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}不傻, 真的。{\r}\NNot so foolish, really.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.00,1:01:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}看这个。{\r}\NLook at this.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.00,1:02:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}看看。{\r}\NGo ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.30,1:02:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}这些是在我登上 Eiger(艾尔格)峰北坡后拍的。{\r}\NThat's after I climbed the Eiger North Face.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.00,1:02:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}这是奥林匹克金牌。 不过没什么。{\r}\NThat's Olympics. Gold medal. Not important.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.50,1:02:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}这就是我们在文化上的另一个巨大差异。{\r}\NThen this is another great difference between our civilization and yours.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.50,1:02:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}你们崇拜。。。{\r}\NYou admire the man...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.40,1:02:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k190}。。。何种职业中勇于攀登顶峰的人,{\r}\Nwho pushes his way to the top in any walk of life...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.60,1:02:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}而我们崇拜放弃自我的人。{\r}\Nwhile we admire the man who abandons his ego.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.70,1:02:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}藏民一般都不会以这种方式生活。{\r}\NThe average Tibetan wouldn't think to thrust himself forward this way.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.90,1:02:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}先生。{\r}\NGentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.30,1:03:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}- 对不起,我们认识吗? - 没有。{\r}\N- I'm sorry. Have we met? - No, we have not.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.00,1:03:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k270}我叫 Ngawang Jigme。{\r}\NI am Ngawang Jigme.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.70,1:03:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}- 哦, 想起来了。 -原谅我们。{\r}\N- Yes, of course. - Forgive us.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.70,1:03:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}谢谢你慷慨的礼物。{\r}\NThank you for your generous gift.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.50,1:03:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k280}非常好。 谢谢。{\r}\NIt's wonderful. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.00,1:03:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}没什么。 我想我们会再见面的。{\r}\NYou are most welcome. I am sure we will meet again.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.80,1:03:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}你或许可以向我们解释。。。{\r}\NPerhaps you could help us explain...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.70,1:03:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}为什么大臣(the ministers)。。。{\r}\Nwhy the min isters...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.90,1:03:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k220}。。。要求中国政府停止。。。{\r}\Ndemand that the Chinese government...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.80,1:03:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}。。。对喇嘛的{\r}\N"...cease making generous financlal contributions...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.70,1:03:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}。。。慷慨经济援助。{\r}\Nto Tibetan monasteries."
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.00,1:03:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我们的援助让你们的政府不高兴吗?{\r}\NDo our gifts displease your government?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.40,1:04:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我不能代表the regent 或者 the ministers说话, 很抱歉。{\r}\NI cannot speak for the regent nor the ministers, Excellence.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.70,1:04:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我只是一个小小的秘书。{\r}\NI am only a mere secretary.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.10,1:04:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k240}不会很久了, 我相信。 请坐。{\r}\NNot for long, I presume. Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.30,1:04:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}一个像你这样极具天赋的人应该不会满足。。。{\r}\NA man of such obvious talent cannot be satisfied...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.80,1:04:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}。。。仅仅翻译信件吧。{\r}\Nwith just translating letters.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.30,1:04:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}你的外交才能。。。{\r}\NYour diplomatic skill...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.50,1:04:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}将在这里收到丰厚的回报。{\r}\Nwould be richly rewarded here.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.50,1:04:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}忠诚的为西藏服务对我来说就足够了, 抱歉。{\r}\NServing my country faithfully is reward enough, Excellence.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.40,1:04:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我现在可以走了吗。{\r}\NI ask permission to take my leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.00,1:05:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}今天我们好像都需要一个好裁缝。{\r}\NIt looks like we're both in need of a good tailor today.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.60,1:06:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}是的, 这有点……{\r}\NYes, there's a--
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.20,1:06:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k260}请坐一会。{\r}\NPlease, take a seat.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.36,1:06:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}你喜欢这个? 我买给你。{\r}\NDo you like these? I'll buy them for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.86,1:06:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k250}谢谢你, 但是我不经常吃肉。{\r}\NThank you, but I don't eat much meat.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.06,1:06:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}- 不吃肉? -他们告诉我这是西方的刀。{\r}\N- Don't eat meat? - He says they are knives from West.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.26,1:06:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}把它穿在脚上用来切肉。{\r}\NYou put them on your feet to cut meat.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.66,1:07:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}这是溜冰鞋。{\r}\NThey are ice skates.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.76,1:07:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k210}穿着可以。。。{\r}\NYou put them on your feet...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.26,1:07:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k250}溜冰。。。{\r}\Nto skate...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.66,1:07:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k140}在冰上滑行-- 就是一种冰上舞蹈。{\r}\Nto glide-- sort of dance on ice.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.46,1:07:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k280}为什么？{\r}\N- Yeah. - Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.56,1:07:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k210}- 为什么不? - 这是另一种傻傻的娱乐。{\r}\N- Why n ot? - It's another fool's pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.86,1:07:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}把它买下。{\r}\NLet's get them. How mu--
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.26,1:07:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}不，是这个?{\r}\NNo, for this?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.96,1:07:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k270}十元。{\r}\NTen.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.26,1:07:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}这个呢?{\r}\NAnd for this?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.76,1:07:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k150}你看见了吗?{\r}\NDid you see?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.66,1:07:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k290}看见了吗?{\r}\NDid you see that?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.76,1:07:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}-你伤着了吗? - 没有, 谢谢你。 我没事。{\r}\N- Did you hurt yourself? - No, thank you. I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.46,1:08:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我们继续。 站起来。{\r}\NHere we go. Up.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.16,1:08:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}- 你没事吧? 有撞着头吗? - 没有,我很开心。{\r}\N- You okay? Did you bang your head? - No, I'm having fun.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.26,1:08:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}- 你必须先要站住。 - 看着我!{\r}\N- You must hold on. - Watch me!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.16,1:08:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}- 只要看着我的眼睛就可以了。 - 对了,就这样。{\r}\N- Do not look too much at the ground. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.56,1:08:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k240}- 不要老盯着地上看。 - 就这样。{\r}\N- Look only lnto my eyes. - Yes, all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.96,1:08:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我能帮你吗? 抓住我的手。{\r}\NCan I help you? Here, take my h and.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.36,1:08:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}- 开心吗? - 非常开心。{\r}\N- Are you happy? - Very happy.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.86,1:09:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我试着去想你的样子, Rolf。。。{\r}\NI try to picture you, Rolf...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.86,1:09:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我看见:{\r}\Nand this is what I see:
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.56,1:09:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k270}一个健壮聪明的男孩。。。{\r}\Na young boy who is strong and bright...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.26,1:09:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}对生活充满好奇。。。{\r}\Na boy filled with curioslty about llfe...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.26,1:09:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}勇于从失败中吸取教训。{\r}\Na boy who lsn't afraid to learn from his mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.16,1:10:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}你好,结婚的女人。{\r}\NHello, married woman.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.26,1:10:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}你好。单身的男人。{\r}\NHello. bachelor man. .
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.06,1:10:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}恭喜。{\r}\NCongratulations.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.06,1:10:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}进屋吧。{\r}\NWell. come in. .
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.46,1:10:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}日本人正在面对越来越强大的挑战。。。{\r}\NThe Japanese army is facing a growing challenge...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.76,1:10:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}这种挑战不是来自中国的正面战场。。。{\r}\Nnot from China 's unified front...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.26,1:10:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k250}而是来自在毛泽东领导下的。。。{\r}\Nbut from the powerful Chinese Communist Army.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.56,1:10:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k230}强大的共产党军队。{\r}\NUnder the control of Mao Tse-tung--
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.16,1:10:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}有谣言说:共产党已经控制了。。。{\r}\NThe rumor is that the Communists have taken over...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.86,1:10:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}整个中国北方。{\r}\Nthe whole of North and Central China.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.66,1:10:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k280}谣言? 这是事实。{\r}\NRumor? It's a fact.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.66,1:10:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k200}从Ngawang那里 我能得到所有关于中国战场的最新消息。{\r}\NNgawang keeps me up-to-date on all China's war news.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.66,1:11:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}Kungo Tsarong一家近来怎么样?{\r}\NSo, how are things at Kungo Tsarong's?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.36,1:11:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}坦白的说我也不知道。 5个月前我就搬出去了。{\r}\NFrankly, I wouldn't know. I moved out five months ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.86,1:11:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}真的? 我们有那么长时间没有见面了?{\r}\NReally? Has it been this long since we have seen you?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.36,1:11:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}- 当然了。 - 最近忙吗?{\r}\N- Apparently it h as. - And have you been busy?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.56,1:11:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}自从他们雇我 勘测整个拉萨城以后。。。{\r}\NThis is why I'm extremely busy...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.66,1:11:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我就非常忙。{\r}\Nsince I've been hired to survey the entire clty of Lhasa.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.06,1:11:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}你们住得太远了, 甚至不在我的地图的范围内。{\r}\NUnfortunately, your place is too far out for me to include it on my map.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.36,1:11:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我们喜欢安静。{\r}\NWe like our privacy.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.26,1:11:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}显然是这样的。{\r}\NYes, apparently so.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.36,1:11:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}关于女人呢? 你遇到喜欢的了吗?{\r}\NWhat about women? Have you met anyone you like?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.76,1:11:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}女人,{\r}\NWomen.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.26,1:11:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k150}由于经历与一个奥地利女人的悲惨婚姻;{\r}\NSince I failed miserably with an Austrlan wife...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.56,1:11:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}与一个似乎被误导了的西藏女人的异国感情失败{\r}\Nan exotic failure with a Tibetan wife seems misguided.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.16,1:11:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k260}我的答案是:没有,我没有遇到过。 你呢?{\r}\NBut to answer your question, no, I haven't. You?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.56,1:12:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}你应该祝福我们,{\r}\NA friend's good fortune is a blessing.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.56,1:12:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我很难过你憎恨我们。{\r}\NI'm sorry you resent ours.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.66,1:12:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}你一定非常孤独、悲伤。{\r}\NYou must be very lonely and sad.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.26,1:12:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}战争结束了!{\r}\NThe war is over!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.36,1:12:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k210}共产党赢了?{\r}\NHave the Communists won?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.16,1:12:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k180}你们的战争, 战争。 德国人投降了。{\r}\NYour war, my friend. Germany has surrendered.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.36,1:12:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}- 你去哪? - 回家,奥地利。{\r}\N- Where are you going? - Back home. Austria.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.06,1:13:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}Harrer先生, 信。{\r}\NMr. Harrer, letter.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.86,1:13:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我们会想念你的 。{\r}\NWe miss you .
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.66,1:13:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我也会想念你们。{\r}\NI miss you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.06,1:13:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}"亲爱的Helnrich Harrer先生:{\r}\N"Dear Mr. Helnrich Harrer:
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.66,1:13:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k260}你不是我的爸爸。{\r}\NYou are not my father.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.16,1:13:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k250}请不要再给我写信了。{\r}\NPlease stop writing me letters.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.76,1:13:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}Rolf lmmendorf。"{\r}\NRolf lmmendorf."
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.56,1:14:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}尊敬的Harry Harrer先生?{\r}\NHonorable Harry Harrer?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.96,1:14:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}- 什么事? - 有你的信。{\r}\N- Yes? - A letter for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.16,1:14:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}尊敬的Heinrich Harrer先生 不想再要任何信件。{\r}\NThe Honorable Heinrich Harrer doesn't want any more letters.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.76,1:14:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}是达赖喇嘛的妈妈写给你的。{\r}\NIt is from the Great Mother of His Holiness, the Dalai Lama.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.66,1:15:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}谢谢你能来,  Harrer 先生。{\r}\NThank you for comlng, Mr. Harrer.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.76,1:15:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k210}感谢您的邀请, Great mother。{\r}\NThank you for inviting me, Great Mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.36,1:15:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}你知道关于我儿子的一些规矩吗?{\r}\NDo you know the rules of protocol concerning my son?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.16,1:15:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}不太清楚-- 我只知道见到他时要鞠躬,伏地跪拜。{\r}\NNot exact-- I know one bows and performs prostrations.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.66,1:15:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}当达赖喇嘛(His Holiness：尊称) 在场的时候{\r}\NWhen you are in the presence of His Holiness...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.36,1:15:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k270}你必须一直弯腰站着。。。{\r}\Nyou must always be standing...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.66,1:15:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k230}双手合十。{\r}\Nbent in obeisance, hands folded in supplication.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.66,1:15:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}如果坐着, 必须比他坐得底。{\r}\NIf seated, you must always be seated lower than he.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.66,1:15:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}永远不要看他的眼睛。 不要先于他说话。{\r}\NNever look him in the eye. Never speak before he does.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.86,1:15:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}把他称作 "Your Holiness"(宗教领袖的尊称)。{\r}\NAlways refer to him as "Your Holiness."
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.96,1:15:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}不要背朝他。 永远不要去碰他。 。{\r}\NNever turn your back to him. And never. never touch him. .
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.96,1:16:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}他是 Avalokiteshvara菩萨 (一种极富同情心的菩萨)。。。{\r}\NHe is the reincarnation of Avalokiteshvara...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.56,1:16:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}的转世。{\r}\Nthe Bodhisattva of Compassion.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.16,1:16:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}在他加冕之后, 他将被称作。。。{\r}\NAfter his recognition, he was renamed...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.16,1:16:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}Jetsun Jamphel Ngawang Lobsang Yeshi Tenzin Gyatso。。。{\r}\NJetsun Jamphel Ngawang Lobsang Yeshi Tenzin Gyatso...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.26,1:16:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}神圣, 无上, 雄辩, 怜世。。。{\r}\NHoly Lord, Gentle Glory, Eloquent, Compassionate...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.16,1:16:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}的信仰守护神及大智者。{\r}\NLearned Defender of the Faith , Ocean of Wisdom.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.06,1:16:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}达赖喇嘛很想见你,{\r}\NHis Holiness, the Dalai Lama, would like to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.26,1:16:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}但是他的导师不允许你们私下见面。。。{\r}\NAs his advisors have not permitted a private audlence with you...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.86,1:16:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}所以他让我带你去参加我们母子每月一次的探望。{\r}\NHis Holiness has asked me to bring you along to my monthly audience.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:52.06,1:16:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我很荣幸能前往。{\r}\NI'd be honored and moved.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.76,1:18:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}黄头发。{\r}\NYellow head.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.76,1:19:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}你的胳膊上也有毛吗? 腿上呢?{\r}\NYou have hair on your arms too? And legs?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.66,1:19:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}- 你呢? - Harrer先生。{\r}\N- How about you? - Mr. Harrer.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.66,1:19:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}见到你真荣幸, Your Holiness。{\r}\NIt's an honor to meet you, Your Holiness.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.86,1:19:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}你喜欢看电影吗?{\r}\NDo you like movies?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.06,1:19:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}你知道我已经有八年没看电影了。{\r}\NYou know, I haven't seen a movie in about eight years.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.26,1:19:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k220}-但是当我回想起来的时候,我还是非常喜欢看电影的。 - 我也是。{\r}\N- But as I recall, yes, very much. - So do l.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.96,1:19:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}- 太好了。 - 我有一个放映机,还有一些电影。{\r}\N- I'm glad to hear that. - I have a movie projector. And films.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.86,1:20:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我想让你帮我在这里建个电影院。{\r}\NI want to build a movie house. Here. at the Potala. .
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.16,1:20:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}- 要有座位,设施齐全。 - 有座位,可以呀。{\r}\N- With seats and everything. - Seats would be advisable.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.66,1:20:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}你会建吗?{\r}\NCan you build it?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.96,1:20:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}-什么? - 你能够帮我建一个电影院吗?{\r}\N- Excuse me? - Can you build a movie house for me?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.56,1:20:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k260}我的导师不会不同意, 你也会得到大笔报酬。{\r}\NMy advisors cannot disapprove, and you wIll be well paid.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.56,1:20:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}那你就必须每天到这里来建电影院, 每一天。{\r}\NAnd you will have to come here every day to build it, every single day.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.76,1:20:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}你在这里的时候就可以来看我。 我们可以讨论很多话题。{\r}\NWhen you are here, you'll visit me. We can have conversations on many toplcs.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.96,1:20:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我想了解你们的世界。{\r}\NI would like to learn about the world you come from.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.76,1:20:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k280}举个例子, 巴黎在哪,法国在哪? 什么是燃烧弹?{\r}\NFor example, where is Paris, France? And what's a Molotov cocktall?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.66,1:20:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}谁是开膛手杰克?Jack the Ripper (1888发生在伦敦的连环杀人案件,至今未侦破){\r}\NAnd who i s Jack the Ripper?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.66,1:20:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}你可以告诉我很多事情。{\r}\NYou can tell me many things.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.26,1:20:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我很荣幸能为您效劳。{\r}\NI'm proud to be of servlce, Your Holiness.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.06,1:21:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}出什么事了?{\r}\NWhat is the problem?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.36,1:21:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}蠕虫。{\r}\NWorms.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.66,1:21:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k130}请不要再伤害蠕虫了。{\r}\NPlease, no more hurtlng worms.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.26,1:21:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k260}- 蠕虫?{\r}\N- Please. - Worms?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.46,1:21:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k220}在你的前生,这无罪的蠕虫可能是你的妈妈。{\r}\NIn a past life, thls innocent worm could have been your mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.66,1:21:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}不要再伤害他们了。{\r}\NPlease, no more h urting.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.56,1:21:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k190}这不可能。  请不要再伤害了。{\r}\NIt's impossible. Please, no more.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.46,1:21:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}但是你应该知道, 藏民相信。。。{\r}\NBut you see, Tibetans believe...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.86,1:21:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k240}所有的动物都可能是你前世的妈妈。{\r}\Nall living creatures were their mothers in a past life.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.46,1:21:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}因此我们必须尊重并报答他们。。{\r}\NSo we must show them respect and repay their kindness.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.96,1:21:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}再也不要伤害任何动物了。{\r}\NAnd never, never harm anything that lives.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.86,1:21:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}你无法让那些虔诚的信徒不遵守那些珍贵的教义。{\r}\NYou can't ask a devout people to disregard a precious teaching.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:46.46,1:21:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}是的, 但是。。。{\r}\NYes, but Your Holin ess...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.86,1:21:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我真的尊重, 但我们不可能--{\r}\Nwith true respect, we can't possibly--
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.06,1:21:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}但是我们不可能保护所有的蠕虫。。。{\r}\NI'm sorry, but we can't possibly rescue all the worms...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.76,1:22:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k270}否则的话这辈子电影院也建不成。{\r}\Nnot if you want a theater finished in this lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.66,1:22:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k290}你很聪明,你会有办法的。{\r}\NYou have a clever mind. Think of a solution.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.96,1:22:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}现在顺便告诉我： 电梯是什么东西？{\r}\NAnd in the meantime, you can explaln to me what is an elevator.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.26,1:22:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}南极洲。 在下面。{\r}\NAntarctica. That's down below.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.56,1:22:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}这里。{\r}\NHere.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.86,1:22:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}棒极了。{\r}\NFantastic.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.46,1:23:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}英格兰。{\r}\NEnglan d.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.76,1:23:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}别向我求助。{\r}\NDon't look at me for h elp.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.56,1:23:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}这儿?{\r}\NHere?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.76,1:23:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}加速。{\r}\NShift.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.46,1:23:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}嘿，我认识他。 你好，Honk！{\r}\NOh, I know him. Honk. Hello!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.36,1:23:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}转弯!{\r}\NTurn !
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.36,1:23:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}刹车!{\r}\NBrake!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.46,1:24:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}大臣(a minister)的藏袍 比你原来的褐色藏袍精致多了,是吗?{\r}\NThe robe of a minister is so much finer than your old brown robe, i sn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.66,1:24:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}请。{\r}\NPlease.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.26,1:24:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k160}大家都请坐下。{\r}\NEveryone, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.56,1:24:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k230}提升的那么快。你一定是非常精干了。{\r}\NYou must be very clever to get such a good promotion.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.06,1:24:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我从没想过要一辈子当秘书。{\r}\NI did not intend to be a secretary forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.56,1:24:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k250}显而易见。{\r}\NApparently so.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.96,1:24:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k240}祝贺你。{\r}\NWell , congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.56,1:24:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}不祥的征兆!{\r}\NEvil omen !
Dialogue: 0,1:24:45.46,1:24:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}北京中央消息。。。{\r}\NFrom his headquarters in Peking...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.76,1:24:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}毛泽东主席是当之无愧的。。。{\r}\Nthe Chairman, Mao Tse-tung, was triumphantly proclaimed leader...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.96,1:24:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}新中国的领导者。{\r}\Nof the new People 's Republic of China.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.96,1:25:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}毛主席承诺共产主义政权的第一个任务就是。。。{\r}\NChairman Mao vowed that the first task of the Communist regime...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.06,1:25:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}重新统一中国大陆。{\r}\Nis to reunite the Chinese motherland.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.36,1:25:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}他宣布遥远的西藏。。。{\r}\NHe declared that the remote kingdom of Tibet...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.46,1:25:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}也是中国领土不可分割的一部分。。。{\r}\NIs an lntegral part of the Chinese territory...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.56,1:25:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}因此必须加入新的共和国。{\r}\Nand must join the great new republic.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.66,1:25:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k210}“。。。必须加入新的共和国。”{\r}\N"...and must join the great n ew republic."
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.16,1:25:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k250}中华人民共和国必须知道：{\r}\NPeople's Republic of China is advised...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.86,1:25:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}西藏政府不承认任何外国政权对其具有管辖权{\r}\Nthe government of Tibet recognizes no foreign sovereign.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.06,1:25:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我们是一个独立的国家。{\r}\NWe are an independent nation.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.66,1:25:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k260}所有的中国官员都将被驱逐出西藏。{\r}\NAll the Chinese officials will be expelled from the borders of Tibet.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.26,1:25:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}祝你们回国愉快。{\r}\NWe wish you a happy return to your h omeland.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.26,1:25:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k200}一路顺风。{\r}\NHave a safe and pleasant journey back to China.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.16,1:25:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}一路顺风。{\r}\NMay you have a safe and pleasant journey back to China.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.86,1:25:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}回国愉快。{\r}\NWe wish you a happy return to your homeland.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.66,1:25:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}祝你开心，事业兴旺发达。{\r}\NMay you have happiness and prosperity.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.66,1:25:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}让我看看。{\r}\NLet me see.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.66,1:26:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}你的生命线和长，不像这里的其他人。。{\r}\NYou have a very long lifeline, unlike others here.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:59.16,1:27:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}当我们在朝向太阳时， 就是白天，对不对？{\r}\NWhen we are faclng the light, it's day, yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.56,1:27:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}当我们在阴面的时候, 就是晚上。{\r}\NWhen we are in shadow, it's night.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:05.16,1:27:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k260}所以当拉萨日出的时候。。。{\r}\NSo if the sun is just rising in Lhasa...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.06,1:27:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}这就意味着。。。{\r}\Nthat means it is just setting...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.96,1:27:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k290}纽约大概是日落的时候。{\r}\Nin New York City, perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.46,1:27:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}这就是世界各地的时间各不相同的原因。{\r}\NThat's why it can't be the same time in every place.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:19.96,1:27:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}- 明白了? - 嗯!{\r}\N- Does that answer your question? - Yes!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.86,1:27:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}再多告诉我一些。{\r}\NTell me more.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:57.16,1:27:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}你现在还想知道什么?{\r}\NWhat else do you want to know?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.66,1:28:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}再过一会你将进入 奇妙的大众传媒的世界。{\r}\NIn a few moments, you wIll be entering the world of mass media.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.96,1:28:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我能听见来自世界各地的新闻?{\r}\NI can hear news from all over the planet?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.46,1:28:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k250}我不知道汤加群岛上是否也有电台,{\r}\NI don't know if they have live broadcasts from the Tonga lslands...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.36,1:28:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k290}但是一般来说, 是的。{\r}\Nbut generally speaking, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.96,1:28:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}你听来自你祖国的新闻吗?{\r}\NDo you listen to news from your country?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.96,1:28:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}奥地利? 不,不常听。{\r}\NFrom Austri a? No, not really.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:21.06,1:28:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}照一下, Ku-Dun。{\r}\NGive me some light, Ku-Dun.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:23.16,1:28:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k210}- 为什么?那是你的家。 - 不再是了。{\r}\N- Why? It's your home. - Not anymore It isn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.76,1:28:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}你在那里有朋友和家庭吗?{\r}\NBut don't you have friends and family there?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.56,1:28:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k280}有几个朋友, 没有家。{\r}\NA few friends, no family.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.86,1:28:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}照着不要动, Your Holiness。{\r}\NKeep the light steady, Your Holiness.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.26,1:28:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}为什么? 家人都死了?{\r}\NWhy? ls everyone dead?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.06,1:28:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}你怎么有那么多问题?{\r}\NDo you know there's another sentence construction aside from the question?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:49.46,1:28:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我结过婚,但是离婚了。{\r}\NI was married, but I'm divorced.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:53.76,1:28:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}你做了什么?{\r}\NWhat did you do?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.26,1:29:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我不想要孩子, 于是跑去爬山。{\r}\NI didn't want a child, so I ran away to climb a mountain.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.26,1:29:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}你有孩子?{\r}\NYou h ave a child?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.56,1:29:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}但从来没见过。{\r}\NAlthough I've never seen hlm.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.96,1:29:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}好了,现在让我演示一下, 它是怎么工作的。{\r}\NAll right. Let me show you how this thing works.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:37.86,1:29:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}-就这样别乱动。 -好的, Harrer 先生。{\r}\N- Glve it all you've got. - Yes, Mr. Harrer.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.16,1:30:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}圣诞快乐。{\r}\NHappy Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:24.66,1:30:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k250}谢谢。{\r}\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:38.06,1:30:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}-这是什么特别的日子? - 圣诞节。{\r}\N- What is this special occasion? - This is Chrlstmas.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:41.56,1:30:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}这是给你的,朋友。 拿着。{\r}\NAnd this is for you, my friend. Go on.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:33.36,1:31:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我在 Barkhor 一家店里找到它的。{\r}\N"I found it in a shop in the Barkhor.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:36.16,1:31:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k280}经过一段漫长的旅行之后它回家了。{\r}\NIt has traveled a long way and finally come back home.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.96,1:31:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}感谢你的友谊 Heinrich。{\r}\NThank you for your friendshlp. Heinrich. "
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.46,1:32:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}不可思议。{\r}\NIt is incredible.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.36,1:32:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}谢谢你救了我的命。{\r}\NThank you for saving my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.66,1:32:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}。。。必须从宗教压迫中解放。{\r}\N...must be liberated from religlous oppressors.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.46,1:32:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k280}西藏人民。。。{\r}\NTibetans must be reunited...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.56,1:32:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k210}-必须和新中国大家庭的兄弟姐妹。。。 -关掉它。{\r}\N- with their brothers and sisters... - Turn that off.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:31.46,1:32:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k190}- 团结起来。 - 对不起。{\r}\N- of the great family of new China. - I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:34.66,1:32:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}外国人控制了腐败的西藏政府。{\r}\NForeigners control Tibet's corrupt government.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:37.76,1:32:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}西藏的同志们必须从帝国主义的压迫中解放出来。{\r}\NOur Tibetan comrades must be liberated from foreign imperialists.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:42.26,1:32:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}西藏的百万农奴必须解放。{\r}\NTibet 's million serfs must be freed.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.36,1:32:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}西藏有多少外国人?{\r}\NHow many foreigners are there in Tibet?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:48.46,1:32:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}你和Heinrich。{\r}\NYou, Heinrich.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.06,1:32:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k260}西藏将会解放。{\r}\NTibet will be liberated.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:56.16,1:33:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}他要见你, Harrer先生。{\r}\NHe asked for you, Mr. Harrer.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.26,1:34:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}他们毁灭了我出生的城市——Takster in Amdo。{\r}\NThey were destroying the village I was born in, Takster in Amdo.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.46,1:34:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}真恐怖。{\r}\NIt was terrible.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:20.86,1:34:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k240}这只是梦。 你做了个恶梦而已。{\r}\NIt was just a dream. You had a bad dream. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:24.66,1:34:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}但那是如此真实。 它们从哪来?{\r}\NBut it was so real. Where did it come from?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:29.76,1:34:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我无法想象如此恐怖的事情。{\r}\NMy mind could never imagine such terrible things.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:16.66,1:35:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我睡不着。 害怕恶梦会再回来{\r}\NI can't sleep. I'm afraid the dream will come back.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:24.26,1:35:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}失眠。{\r}\NA couple of insomniacs.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.76,1:35:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}给我讲个故事。{\r}\NTell me a story.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:34.36,1:35:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}讲一个关于爬山的故事{\r}\NTell me a story about cllmbing mountains.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:36.76,1:35:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}这是催眠的好方法。 那些故事连我都烦。{\r}\NThat's one way to fall asleep. Those stories bore even me.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:41.96,1:35:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}那么告诉我你爱什么。{\r}\NThen tell me what you love about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:44.26,1:35:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k230}是什么呢--{\r}\NWhat--
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.96,1:35:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}一定是简单。 那是我的最爱。{\r}\NThe absolute simplicity. That's what I love.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:54.16,1:35:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}当你爬山的时候, 你特别清醒。。。{\r}\NWhen you're climbing, your mind is clear...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:57.76,1:36:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}没有杂念。{\r}\Nfreed of all confusions.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:00.16,1:36:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k240}你注意力集中。{\r}\NYou have focus.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:03.56,1:36:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}忽然光线变得刺眼。。。{\r}\NAnd suddenly the light becomes sharper...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:07.16,1:36:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}声音变得震耳。。。{\r}\Nsounds are rlcher...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:09.86,1:36:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k270}然后你感觉到。。。{\r}\Nand you are filled with...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:12.56,1:36:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k270}生命的强大。{\r}\Nthe deep, powerful presence of life.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:21.36,1:36:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}在另外一个时刻, 我也曾经有过一次那样的感觉{\r}\NI've only felt that way one other time.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:25.16,1:36:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}什么时候?{\r}\NWhen?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:31.66,1:36:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}见到你的时候, Ku-Dun。{\r}\NIn your presence, Ku-Dun.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:36.16,1:36:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}中国人已经占领了北疆的大部分地区。{\r}\NThe Chinese have already secured much of the northern border regions.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:40.26,1:36:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}他们掠夺村庄, 摧毁寺庙。。。{\r}\NThey have ransacked a village, destroyed the monasteries...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.66,1:36:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}焚烧经文,亵渎神灵。{\r}\Nburnt scriptures and defaced holy relics.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:46.46,1:36:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k280}甚至杀死了一些喇嘛……{\r}\NWe've been told they've even killed some monks--
Dialogue: 0,1:36:48.56,1:36:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k210}-哪个村庄? - Takster in Amdo。{\r}\N- Which vill age? - Takster in Amdo.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:51.86,1:36:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}达赖喇嘛在那里出生。{\r}\NIt's where His Holiness was born.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.06,1:37:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}Go ahead。{\r}\NGo ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:09.76,1:37:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}当你出任前任达赖喇嘛的国防大臣时。。。{\r}\NWhen you were defense minister to the previous Dalai Lama...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:12.76,1:37:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}你想组建军队。{\r}\Nthen you wanted to reorganlze the army.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:15.36,1:37:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k260}你现在可以做吗?{\r}\NCan you do it now?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:17.36,1:37:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k200}人民解放军有百万之众。{\r}\NThe People's Liberation Army is one million troops strong.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:21.96,1:37:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我们只有8000个人50门炮。。。{\r}\NWe have 8,000 men with 50 pieces of artillery...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:25.56,1:37:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}和几百门迫击炮以及一些机枪。{\r}\Nand a few hundred mortars and machine guns.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:28.06,1:37:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k250}这毫无希望。{\r}\NThe task is hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:29.86,1:37:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k180}那你拒绝这个任务了，是吗?{\r}\NThen you refuse the appointment, do you?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.06,1:37:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}不是。 我很荣幸的接受。{\r}\NNo. I accept it with honor.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:38.66,1:37:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}你们两位先生应该了解武器。{\r}\NYou two gentlemen know about wars.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:41.46,1:37:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k280}有什么武器可以推荐?{\r}\NWhat type of weapon do you recommend?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:58.06,1:38:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}中国军队好像正在向我们的北疆挺进。{\r}\NIt seems the Chinese troops are advancing toward our northern borders.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:00.56,1:38:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k250}达赖喇嘛去哪了?{\r}\NWhere's His Holiness?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:03.16,1:38:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k260}大不列颠加冕的荣耀。{\r}\NThe glory of a British coronation.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:05.26,1:38:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k210}这是世界上最隆重的事情。{\r}\NNowhere in the world is there anything half so wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:08.36,1:38:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}你一生中只能见证一次或两次这样的时刻。。。{\r}\NOnly once or twice in the life of each one of us comes such a day as this...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:11.56,1:38:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}当我们意识到 我们正在目睹创造历史。。。{\r}\Nwhen we know that we are watchlng history in the making...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:14.36,1:38:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k280}当我们意识到我们的后代将会想起今天——。。。{\r}\Nwhen we know that generations to come will look back on this day...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:18.26,1:38:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}1937年5月12日, 这一天将注定成为历史。。。{\r}\Nfor May 12, 1937, wIll be one of the dates in hlstory...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.66,1:38:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}或许一千年里孩子们都要学习这段历史。{\r}\Nthat schoolchildren will learn about maybe a thousand years from now.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:25.16,1:38:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}每一刻都令人兴奋发抖……{\r}\NEvery moment the thrill of excitement--
Dialogue: 0,1:38:26.86,1:38:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k170}你觉得会有人在银幕上看见西藏。。。{\r}\NDo you thlnk someday people will look at Tibet on the movie screen...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:31.46,1:38:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}并想知道那里发生了什么?{\r}\Nand wonder what happened to us?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:33.56,1:38:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k210}加冕的四轮大马车向前移动了。{\r}\NThe coronation coach moves forward.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:35.36,1:38:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k180}我不知道。{\r}\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:37.86,1:38:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k250}你不是什么都知道吗?{\r}\NDon't you have all the answers?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.16,1:38:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我不是。{\r}\NI don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:53.46,1:38:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}在藏民传统的聚会的场地上。。。{\r}\NOn the same field where Tibetans traditionally gathered for picnics...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:57.16,1:38:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}正在建造一条飞机跑道。。。{\r}\Nground was cleared to build an alrstrip...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:59.16,1:39:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k200}一边载着中国将军的飞机可以着落。{\r}\Nso that the plane carrying three Chinese generals could land.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:02.76,1:39:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}附近,西藏的军队正在进行机动性训练。{\r}\NNearby, the Tibetan army practiced its maneuvers.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:06.46,1:39:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}一些士兵穿着古老的盔甲。{\r}\NSome of the soldiers wear ancient mesh armour.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:09.26,1:39:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k280}他们把老式的步枪和长矛当作大炮。{\r}\NThey bring old muskets and spears as artillery.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:12.76,1:39:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}这是一幅—— 一个热爱和平的民族正在徒劳的建立一支军队的景象。{\r}\NThe spectacle of a peace-lovlng nation, vainly attempting to create a mllitary.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:18.36,1:39:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我的朋友的脸上对战争的恐惧。。。{\r}\NThe fears of war on my friends ' faces...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:21.66,1:39:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}深深地震撼了每个人的神经。{\r}\Nstrike a deeply burled personal chord.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:26.26,1:39:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我的祖国（德国）的侵略性。。。{\r}\NEchoes of the aggressions of my own country...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:29.06,1:39:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k280}以及征服弱小民族欲望。。。{\r}\Nthe will to overpower weaker peoples...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:32.16,1:39:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}让我感到羞辱。{\r}\Nbring shame to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:35.36,1:39:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}很久以来我想到这些就感到战栗。。。{\r}\NI shudder to recall how once long ago I embraced the same beliefs...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:39.86,1:39:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}事实上。。。{\r}\Nhow at one time I was, in fact...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.96,1:39:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k210}这些狭隘的中国人也在做同样的事情。{\r}\Nno different from these intolerant Chinese.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:47.96,1:39:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}藏民认为敌人是最好的老师。。。{\r}\NThe Tibetans say an enemy is the greatest teacher...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:50.56,1:39:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k260}因为只有敌人可以磨练你的容忍, 让你富有同情心。{\r}\Nbecause only an enemy can help develop patience and compassion.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.76,1:39:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}他们坚信宗教的力量。。。{\r}\NThey believe with rock-llke faith that the power of their religion...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:57.66,1:40:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k290}将保护他们免遭遭难。{\r}\Nwill protect them against these Chinese.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.96,1:40:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}为了迎接中国将军的来访。。。{\r}\NIn preparation for the generals ' visit...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:04.16,1:40:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k220}整个拉萨都在进行神圣的宗教礼仪。{\r}\Nsacred ceremonies are performed throughout Lhasa.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:07.36,1:40:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}人们非常细心的用黄油雕刻神像。{\r}\NSculptures of deities have been carved with great care in butter.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:12.66,1:40:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}当太阳将其熔化时,她提醒人们什么也不存在。{\r}\NAs the sun melts them, they become a reminder that nothlng lasts.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:30.66,1:40:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}冉冉升起的政治新星, 大臣 Ngawang Jigme。。。{\r}\NThe rising star of the cabinet, Minister Ngawang Jigme...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:34.56,1:40:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}自做主张同意中国将军。。。{\r}\Nmade an offering of his own to greet the Chinese generals...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:37.16,1:40:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k260}访问西藏。{\r}\Nand lead them through Lhasa.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:42.36,1:40:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}中国不应该享受升起国旗的荣耀。{\r}\NRaising their flag is an honor the Chinese don't deserve.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:45.36,1:40:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}当你不是足够强大的时候, 你就应该拥抱你的敌人。{\r}\NWhen you are not strong enough to fight, you should embrace your enemy.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:48.96,1:40:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}当他两手抱你的时候, 他就没法用枪指着你了。{\r}\NWith both arms around you, he cannot point a gun at you.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:52.16,1:40:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}在政治上没有什么荣耀可谈。{\r}\NNothing in politics is a matter of honor, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:01.06,1:42:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}即使在天堂历史也会重复。{\r}\NHistory repeats itself, even in paradise.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:07.16,1:42:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}将军,我们将去和达赖喇嘛会面--{\r}\NGeneral, we shall have our audience with His--
Dialogue: 0,1:42:35.96,1:42:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}将军, 僧侣们制作这个沙坛已经很多天了。{\r}\NGeneral, the monks have been making this mandala of sand for many days.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:41.46,1:42:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}它象征启蒙和和平。{\r}\NIt is a symbol of enlightenment and peace.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:44.36,1:42:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k290}将军 !{\r}\NGeneral !
Dialogue: 0,1:42:57.96,1:43:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我们不会比他坐得低。{\r}\NWe do not sit lower than he does.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.76,1:43:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}但是,将军这是我们习惯。{\r}\NBut, General, It is our custom.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:04.56,1:43:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k280}我可以坐在下面。{\r}\NI can sit down there.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:23.26,1:43:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}Your Holiness, 这是张经武将军。。。{\r}\NYour Holiness, this is General Chang Jing Wu...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:26.16,1:43:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k290}Than Gua将军, Than Gua San将军。{\r}\NGeneral Than Gua, General Than Gua San.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:29.56,1:43:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}他们想和你会谈。{\r}\NThey wish to have an audience with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:33.86,1:43:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}祝你们快乐健康。{\r}\NMay you have happiness and prosperity.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:38.66,1:43:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}如果西藏接受中国的政治管辖, 他们保证。。。{\r}\NThey are promising regional autonomy and religious freedom...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:43.36,1:43:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}西藏的宗教自治和信仰自有。{\r}\Nif Tibet accepts that China be its political master.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.66,1:43:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}在我成年以前,  the regent(摄政王)才是西藏的政治领袖 。{\r}\NUntil I attain my majority, the regent ls the political leader of Tibet.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:56.36,1:43:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}你们应该和他去谈这些。。。{\r}\NYou should have requested an audlence with him...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:58.86,1:44:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k250}。。。国家大事。{\r}\Nto discuss these important matters of the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:02.76,1:44:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}这方面我的经验有限,{\r}\NMy experience of such things is limited.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:07.76,1:44:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我只是一个简单的佛教僧侣。{\r}\NI am a simple Buddhist monk.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:10.36,1:44:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k260}我所知道的只有经文和佛所说的。{\r}\NAll I know is the scripture and the words of Lord Buddha.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:15.06,1:44:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}他说：“所有的人都会在 危险和死亡面前颤抖，{\r}\NHe sald, "All beings tremble before danger and death.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:20.36,1:44:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}生命是最珍贵的，{\r}\NLife is dear to all.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:22.36,1:44:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k200}如果人们意识到这一点他就不会杀生。”{\r}\NWhen a man considers this, he does not kill or cause to kill."
Dialogue: 0,1:44:27.26,1:44:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}你们必须知道。{\r}\NYou must understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:29.06,1:44:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k180}这些话深植于每个藏民的心中，{\r}\NThese words are ingrained in the heart of every Tibetan.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:33.86,1:44:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}这就是为什么我们 热爱和平、拒绝暴力。{\r}\NIt ls why we are a peaceful people who reject violence on principle.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:40.96,1:44:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}希望你们能把这一点看作我们最强大的力量。。。{\r}\NI pray you will see this is our greatest strength...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:45.46,1:44:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}而不是弱点。{\r}\Nnot our weakness.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:48.76,1:44:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}感谢你的来访。{\r}\NI thank you for your vislt.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:12.26,1:45:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}宗教是毒药。{\r}\NRellgion is poison.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:22.66,1:46:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}在Den-Go附近中国向西藏边境发起进攻。{\r}\NThe Chinese have attacked the Tlbetan frontier near Den-Go.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:38.66,1:46:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}今天拂晓在张经武将军的指挥下。。。{\r}\N"Today at the dawn, 84,000 troops of the 1st and 2nd Field Armles...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:42.86,1:46:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}第一、二野战军84，000人。。。{\r}\Nunder the overall command of General Chang Jing Wu...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:47.46,1:46:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}在Den－Go附近向西藏发起攻击。{\r}\Nattacked the Tibetan frontier near Den-Go.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:51.16,1:46:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}西藏方面认为中国 对Chamdo的进攻也迫在眉睫。{\r}\NThe Tibetan army believes an attack on Chamdo is imminent.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:55.06,1:46:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}Ngawang Jigme,我们新的代总理。。。{\r}\NNgawang Jigme, our newly appointed governor...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:58.16,1:47:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}正在将部队派往中国部队所在地区。。。{\r}\Nis preparing to send troops toward the Chinese column...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:00.56,1:47:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k240}以阻止他们前进。{\r}\NIn order to stop their progresslon. "
Dialogue: 0,1:47:04.56,1:47:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}如你所知, Chamdo是西藏的大门。{\r}\NAs you know, Chamdo is the gateway to Tibet.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:08.26,1:47:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}如果 Chamdo 失守，西藏就完了。{\r}\NIf Chamdo falls. . the whole of Tibet will fall.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:11.16,1:47:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k290}如果我连这一点都不知道 我就不会是代总理了。{\r}\NIf I did not know that, I would not have been appointed governor.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:14.66,1:47:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}你应该知道我将战斗到最后一个人。{\r}\NYou do realize our troops are committed to fighting the Chinese to the last man.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:20.16,1:47:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}宁愿战死也不投降。{\r}\NThey would rather die than surrender.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:24.06,1:47:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}毫无疑问，只要我在Chamdo 就不会有投降的。{\r}\NRest assured. there will be no surrender . as long as I am in Chamdo.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:51.76,1:50:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}拉萨电台。{\r}\NRadio Lh asa.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:55.26,1:50:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}现在{\r}\NNow.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:57.46,1:51:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k220}我们请求投降。{\r}\NWe request permission to surrender.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:00.46,1:51:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}- 但是这里不会有人投降-- - 我说了, “拉萨电台”{\r}\N- But there will be no surrender-- - I said, "Radio Lh asa."
Dialogue: 0,1:51:03.36,1:51:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k290}现在我们请求投降。{\r}\NPermission to surrender now.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:52.56,1:51:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我们11天内输掉了这场战争, Heinrich。{\r}\NWe lost the war in 11 days, Heinrich.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:56.26,1:51:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}投降是对我们最后的宣判。{\r}\NThis surrender is our death sentence.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:00.26,1:52:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我担心我们的朋友 Ngawang Jigme已经出卖了我们。{\r}\NAnd I'm afraid our friend Ngawang Jigme has issued it.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:05.86,1:52:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}他放弃了Chamdo并且炸毁了临时军火库。{\r}\NHe abandoned Chamdo and then destroyed the ammunition dumps.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:12.46,1:52:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}没有武器弹药。。。{\r}\NWithout weapons and ammunition...
Dialogue: 0,1:52:15.96,1:52:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}那些想血拼到底的士兵也无法战斗。{\r}\Nthere was no hope for the troops who wanted to fight.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:20.16,1:52:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}本来我们的游击队可以在山上据守几个月。。。{\r}\NOur guerrillas could have held the mountain passes for months...
Dialogue: 0,1:52:24.36,1:52:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}甚至几年。{\r}\Neven years.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:26.36,1:52:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k200}这样我们就有时间向其他国家求助。{\r}\NIt would have bought us time to make appeals for help to other nations.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:31.36,1:52:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}现在一点希望都没有了。{\r}\NNow it's lost.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:33.86,1:52:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k250}他们毁掉了西藏的大门。{\r}\NThey broke down the gates.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:24.46,1:53:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}你好，老朋友。{\r}\NHello, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:33.46,1:53:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}对于西藏。。。{\r}\NWe did what was the best for our country...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:36.46,1:53:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我们已经做了最好的选择。{\r}\Nfor Tibet.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:39.66,1:53:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}在来拉萨的路上， 我看见藏民穿着这样的夹克。{\r}\NOn the way to Lhasa, I would see Tibetans wearing these jackets.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:44.16,1:53:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}“中国士兵非常好。{\r}\N"Chinese soldiers. Very nice.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:46.36,1:53:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k220}给粮食、衣服、钱，非常好。”{\r}\NGlve food, clothes, money. Very nice."
Dialogue: 0,1:53:50.96,1:53:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}对我来说这有点奇怪—— 像夹克这样平淡无奇的东西。。。{\r}\NIt's strange to me that something so harmless as a jacket...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:54.66,1:53:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}居然暗示了一个巨大的谎言。{\r}\Ncould symbolize such a great lie.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:03.06,1:54:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}经过了这些年，你仍然不明白藏民的习俗。{\r}\NAfter all these years, you still do not understand Tibetan ways.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:07.06,1:54:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}归还别人礼物，是不可宽恕的。。{\r}\NTo return a gift is unforgivable.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:13.66,1:54:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}一个背叛了民族的人没有权力来鼓吹所谓的规则。{\r}\NA man who betrays his culture should not preach about its customs.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:23.86,1:54:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}曾经有一刻，我诅咒你早死。。。{\r}\NThere was a time I would have wished you dead...
Dialogue: 0,1:54:26.86,1:54:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}但是你的羞辱将变成你的痛苦，{\r}\Nbut your shame will be your torture.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:29.16,1:54:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k230}而痛苦将成为你生命的全部，{\r}\NAnd your torture will be your life.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:32.66,1:54:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我希望它越长越好。{\r}\NI wish it to be long.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:46.86,1:54:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我们祈求授予达赖喇嘛权力。。。{\r}\NWe pray that His Holiness, the Dalai Lama...
Dialogue: 0,1:54:49.66,1:54:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k280}去团结他的人民。{\r}\Nwill be granted the power to unify his people.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:53.66,1:54:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我们谨要求西藏政府尊重我们的愿望。。。{\r}\NWe humbly ask the Tibetan government to honor our request...
Dialogue: 0,1:54:58.66,1:55:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}让达赖喇嘛登基。{\r}\Nand let the Dalai Lama attain his political majority.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:57.36,1:56:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}你让大家都急死了。{\r}\NYou have the entire palace in a panlc.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:02.26,1:56:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我只是想躲起来一天而已。{\r}\NI'm hiding from the world for a day.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:08.16,1:56:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}在玻璃房里躲着挺难的，不是吗？{\r}\NKind of difficult in a glasshouse, no?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:16.66,1:56:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}月光曲。。。{\r}\NIt's The Moonlight...
Dialogue: 0,1:56:19.06,1:56:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k240}德彪西的。{\r}\Nby Debussy.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:23.76,1:56:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}关于这首曲子你还知道些什么？{\r}\NWhat else do you know about this song?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:05.36,1:58:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}这匹、这匹还有这匹。{\r}\NHim, him and him.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:20.76,1:58:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我想你已经收到了登基典礼的邀请。{\r}\NI hope you've received your invitation to the enthronement ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:24.76,1:58:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}是的，谢谢。{\r}\NYes. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:26.16,1:58:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k140}- 在下个星期。 - 谢谢你。{\r}\N- It's next week. - Th ank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:42.46,1:58:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我看起来像个老学究吗?{\r}\NDo I look like an egghead?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:45.46,1:58:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}不，眼镜很配你。{\r}\NNo, they suit you.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:50.16,1:58:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}西藏有一种说法。。。{\r}\NWe have a saying in Tibet...
Dialogue: 0,1:58:52.66,1:58:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k250}“如果是一个可以解决的问题，那就没必要担心它；{\r}\N"If the problem can be solved, there is no use worrying about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:57.16,1:59:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}如果是不能解决的问题，担心也没用。{\r}\NIf it can't be solved. . worrying will do no good."
Dialogue: 0,1:59:01.46,1:59:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}所以别担心。{\r}\NSo stop worrying.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:04.36,1:59:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k290}你必须离开西藏，在这里有生命危险。{\r}\NYou have to leave Tibet. Your life's at great risk.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:10.36,1:59:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}请原谅我的冒失， 我已经安排好让你安全离开。{\r}\NForgive my presumption, but I made arrangements to get you out safely.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:15.36,1:59:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我们必须在典礼前离开， 中国人不会接受的。{\r}\NWe should leave after the enthronement. The Chinese would never expect it--
Dialogue: 0,1:59:19.06,1:59:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}如果我逃跑了我怎么帮助这里的人们？ 那我成了什么样的领袖？{\r}\NHow can I help people if I run away from them? What kind of leader would I be?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:26.16,1:59:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我必须留在这里。{\r}\NI have to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:28.56,1:59:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k240}帮助别人就是解放自己。{\r}\NServing others is my path to liberation .
Dialogue: 0,1:59:41.76,1:59:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}-那我也不离开。 - 为什么不?{\r}\N- Then I don't go either. - Why not?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:44.86,1:59:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}因为你是我的自由之路。{\r}\NBecause you are my path to liberation.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:50.26,1:59:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}佛主说：拯救不是源之佛的眼睛，{\r}\NThe Buddha sald. "Salvation . does not come from the slght of me.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:55.46,1:59:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}而是需要你去努力实践，{\r}\NIt demands strenuous effort and practice.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:59.06,2:00:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}勤奋工作并探求自我拯救。{\r}\NSo work hard and seek your own salvation diligently."
Dialogue: 0,2:00:06.56,2:00:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我不是你的儿子。。。{\r}\NI am not your son...
Dialogue: 0,2:00:10.36,2:00:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}也从不把你当父亲看。{\r}\Nand I never thought of you as my father.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:13.56,2:00:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}这个对于我来说，你是太不正式的了。{\r}\NYou were much too informal with me for that.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:28.56,2:00:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}你想他吗?{\r}\NDo you ever think about him?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:45.16,2:00:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}想什么?{\r}\NAnd wh at do you think about?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:58.76,2:01:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}这真的不是有意识地去想。{\r}\NIt's not the conscious thought really.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:02.66,2:01:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}他总是在那里。{\r}\NIt's just always there.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:13.56,2:01:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我穿越西藏时，他就在身边；{\r}\NWhen I crossed Tibet, he was with me.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:16.86,2:01:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我来到拉萨，他在我身边；{\r}\NWhen I came to Lhasa. . he was with me.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:19.36,2:01:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k250}我坐在你旁边时， 他。。。{\r}\NWhen I sit beside you, he's...
Dialogue: 0,2:01:23.56,2:01:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}也在我身边。{\r}\Nthere with me.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:29.86,2:01:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我甚至不能想象没有他， 这个世界会变成什么样。{\r}\NI can't even imagine how I pictured the world without him in it.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:37.06,2:01:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}所以你应该回家，去做他的父亲。{\r}\NThen you should go home and be his father.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:47.46,2:01:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我知道。{\r}\NI know.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:51.06,2:01:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}你在这里的任务已经完成了。{\r}\NYou have finished your job with me.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:56.86,2:01:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}但是你必须留下来参加即位典礼。{\r}\NBut you have to stay for my enthronement.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:59.06,2:02:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k220}你可以看见华丽、荣耀的我。{\r}\NI want you to see me in all my pomp and glory.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:05.66,2:02:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}非常荣幸。{\r}\NIt'd be a pleasure, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:26.56,2:03:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}西藏政府。。。{\r}\NFrom the government of Tibet...
Dialogue: 0,2:03:28.76,2:03:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k220}十四世达赖喇嘛。。。{\r}\Nto Your Holin ess, the fourteenth Dalai Lama...
Dialogue: 0,2:03:31.36,2:03:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k260}作为西藏精神和万物的领袖。。。{\r}\Nwe ask you to rule your people...
Dialogue: 0,2:03:33.36,2:03:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k200}我们请求您普渡众生。{\r}\Nas the spiritual and temporal leader of Tibet.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:43.76,2:03:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}据你们的祈祷和愿望 我谨接受。{\r}\NBy your prayers and wishes, I humbly accept.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:43.76,2:04:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}奶茶，我从来都不喜欢。{\r}\NButter tea. It was never my cup of tea.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:49.96,2:04:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}-一杯足够了。 - 是的，但我们必须入乡随俗。{\r}\N- One was enough. - Yes, we must follow the custom.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:54.26,2:04:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}一杯热茶送亲人。{\r}\NA fresh cup of tea is poured for the loved one departing.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:03.86,2:05:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}不要动它， 等他回来再喝。{\r}\NIt sits untouched, walting for hls return.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:09.46,2:06:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}愿所有的旅行者快乐相伴，{\r}\NMay all travelers find happiness wherever they go.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:13.66,2:06:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}心想事成，{\r}\NWithout any effort may they accomplish whatever they set out to do.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:18.86,2:06:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}平安到达，{\r}\NAnd having safely returned to the shore...
Dialogue: 0,2:06:22.26,2:06:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}家人重聚。。{\r}\Nmay they be joyfully reunited with their relatives.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:38.66,2:06:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}Harrer先生{\r}\NMr. Harrer...
Dialogue: 0,2:06:44.06,2:06:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}His Holiness达赖喇嘛给你的。{\r}\Nfrom His Holiness.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:18.36,2:08:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}- 你好 Horst。 -你好 Heinrich。{\r}\N- Hello, Horst. - Hello, Heinrich.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:20.96,2:08:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k260}Rolf,出来见见他。{\r}\NRolf, come out to meet him.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:24.76,2:08:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}不，我不想。。{\r}\NNo, I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:29.36,2:08:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}我可以进去吗？{\r}\NMay l ?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:10.56,2:10:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}Rolf，抓紧时间。{\r}\NRolf, take your time.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:30.26,2:10:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}干得好，儿子。{\r}\NWell done, son.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:33.46,2:10:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20}{\k300}干得好。{\r}\NWell done.
